92static void bytecpy(uint8_t *target, uint8_t *source)
93{
94 if ((target != NULL) && (source != NULL))
95 {
96 *target = *source;
97 }

111float_t lsm6dsox_from_fs2_to_mg(int16_t lsb)
112{
113 return ((float_t)lsb) * 0.061f;
114}
115
116float_t lsm6dsox_from_fs4_to_mg(int16_t lsb)
117{
118 return ((float_t)lsb) * 0.122f;
119}

122{
123 return ((float_t)lsb) * 0.244f;
124}

126float_t lsm6dsox_from_fs16_to_mg(int16_t lsb)
127{
128 return ((float_t)lsb) * 0.488f;
129}

156float_t lsm6dsox_from_lsb_to_celsius(int16_t lsb)
157{
158 return (((float_t)lsb / 256.0f) + 25.0f);
159}

161float_t lsm6dsox_from_lsb_to_nsec(int16_t lsb)
162{
163 return ((float_t)lsb * 25000.0f);
164}

186int32_t lsm6dsox_xl_full_scale_set(stmdev_ctx_t *ctx,
187 lsm6dsox_fs_xl_t val)
188{
189 lsm6dsox_ctrl1_xl_t reg;
190 int32_t ret;
191
192 ret = lsm6dsox_read_reg(ctx, LSM6DSOX_CTRL1_XL, (uint8_t *)&reg, 1);
193
194 if (ret == 0)
195 {
196 reg.fs_xl = (uint8_t) val;
197 ret = lsm6dsox_write_reg(ctx, LSM6DSOX_CTRL1_XL, (uint8_t *)&reg, 1);
198 }
199
200 return ret;
201}
202
211int32_t lsm6dsox_xl_full_scale_get(stmdev_ctx_t *ctx,
212 lsm6dsox_fs_xl_t *val)
213{
214 lsm6dsox_ctrl1_xl_t reg;
215 int32_t ret;
216
217 ret = lsm6dsox_read_reg(ctx, LSM6DSOX_CTRL1_XL, (uint8_t *)&reg, 1);
218
219 switch (reg.fs_xl)
220 {
221 case LSM6DSOX_2g:
222 *val = LSM6DSOX_2g;
223 break;
224
225 case LSM6DSOX_16g:
226 *val = LSM6DSOX_16g;
227 break;
228
229 case LSM6DSOX_4g:
230 *val = LSM6DSOX_4g;
231 break;
232
233 case LSM6DSOX_8g:
234 *val = LSM6DSOX_8g;
235 break;
236
237 default:
238 *val = LSM6DSOX_2g;
239 break;
240 }
241
242 return ret;
243}

253int32_t lsm6dsox_xl_data_rate_set(stmdev_ctx_t *ctx,
254 lsm6dsox_odr_xl_t val)
255{
256 lsm6dsox_odr_xl_t odr_xl = val;
257 lsm6dsox_emb_fsm_enable_t fsm_enable;
258 lsm6dsox_fsm_odr_t fsm_odr;
259 lsm6dsox_emb_sens_t emb_sens;
260 lsm6dsox_mlc_odr_t mlc_odr;
261 lsm6dsox_ctrl1_xl_t reg;
262 int32_t ret;
263
264 /* Check the Finite State Machine data rate constraints */
265 ret = lsm6dsox_fsm_enable_get(ctx, &fsm_enable);
266
267 if (ret == 0)
268 {
269 if ((fsm_enable.fsm_enable_a.fsm1_en |
270 fsm_enable.fsm_enable_a.fsm2_en |
271 fsm_enable.fsm_enable_a.fsm3_en |
272 fsm_enable.fsm_enable_a.fsm4_en |
273 fsm_enable.fsm_enable_a.fsm5_en |
274 fsm_enable.fsm_enable_a.fsm6_en |
275 fsm_enable.fsm_enable_a.fsm7_en |
276 fsm_enable.fsm_enable_a.fsm8_en |
277 fsm_enable.fsm_enable_b.fsm9_en |
278 fsm_enable.fsm_enable_b.fsm10_en |
279 fsm_enable.fsm_enable_b.fsm11_en |
280 fsm_enable.fsm_enable_b.fsm12_en |
281 fsm_enable.fsm_enable_b.fsm13_en |
282 fsm_enable.fsm_enable_b.fsm14_en |
283 fsm_enable.fsm_enable_b.fsm15_en |
284 fsm_enable.fsm_enable_b.fsm16_en) == PROPERTY_ENABLE)
285 {
286 ret = lsm6dsox_fsm_data_rate_get(ctx, &fsm_odr);
287
288 if (ret == 0)
289 {
290 switch (fsm_odr)
291 {
292 case LSM6DSOX_ODR_FSM_12Hz5:
293 if (val == LSM6DSOX_XL_ODR_OFF)
294 {
295 odr_xl = LSM6DSOX_XL_ODR_12Hz5;
296 }
297
298 else
299 {
300 odr_xl = val;
301 }
302
303 break;
304
305 case LSM6DSOX_ODR_FSM_26Hz:
306 if (val == LSM6DSOX_XL_ODR_OFF)
307 {
308 odr_xl = LSM6DSOX_XL_ODR_26Hz;
309 }
310
311 else if (val == LSM6DSOX_XL_ODR_12Hz5)
312 {
313 odr_xl = LSM6DSOX_XL_ODR_26Hz;
314 }
315
316 else
317 {
318 odr_xl = val;
319 }
320
321 break;
322
323 case LSM6DSOX_ODR_FSM_52Hz:
324 if (val == LSM6DSOX_XL_ODR_OFF)
325 {
326 odr_xl = LSM6DSOX_XL_ODR_52Hz;
327 }
328
329 else if (val == LSM6DSOX_XL_ODR_12Hz5)
330 {
331 odr_xl = LSM6DSOX_XL_ODR_52Hz;
332 }
333
334 else if (val == LSM6DSOX_XL_ODR_26Hz)
335 {
336 odr_xl = LSM6DSOX_XL_ODR_52Hz;
337 }
338
339 else
340 {
341 odr_xl = val;
342 }
343
344 break;
345
346 case LSM6DSOX_ODR_FSM_104Hz:
347 if (val == LSM6DSOX_XL_ODR_OFF)
348 {
349 odr_xl = LSM6DSOX_XL_ODR_104Hz;
350 }
351
352 else if (val == LSM6DSOX_XL_ODR_12Hz5)
353 {
354 odr_xl = LSM6DSOX_XL_ODR_104Hz;
355 }
356
357 else if (val == LSM6DSOX_XL_ODR_26Hz)
358 {
359 odr_xl = LSM6DSOX_XL_ODR_104Hz;
360 }
361
362 else if (val == LSM6DSOX_XL_ODR_52Hz)
363 {
364 odr_xl = LSM6DSOX_XL_ODR_104Hz;
365 }
366
367 else
368 {
369 odr_xl = val;
370 }
371
372 break;
373
374 default:
375 odr_xl = val;
376 break;
377 }
378 }
379 }
380 }
381
382 /* Check the Machine Learning Core data rate constraints */
383 emb_sens.mlc = PROPERTY_DISABLE;
384
385 if (ret == 0)
386 {
387 lsm6dsox_embedded_sens_get(ctx, &emb_sens);
388
389 if (emb_sens.mlc == PROPERTY_ENABLE)
390 {
391 ret = lsm6dsox_mlc_data_rate_get(ctx, &mlc_odr);
392
393 if (ret == 0)
394 {
395 switch (mlc_odr)
396 {
397 case LSM6DSOX_ODR_PRGS_12Hz5:
398 if (val == LSM6DSOX_XL_ODR_OFF)
399 {
400 odr_xl = LSM6DSOX_XL_ODR_12Hz5;
401 }
402
403 else
404 {
405 odr_xl = val;
406 }
407
408 break;
409
410 case LSM6DSOX_ODR_PRGS_26Hz:
411 if (val == LSM6DSOX_XL_ODR_OFF)
412 {
413 odr_xl = LSM6DSOX_XL_ODR_26Hz;
414 }
415
416 else if (val == LSM6DSOX_XL_ODR_12Hz5)
417 {
418 odr_xl = LSM6DSOX_XL_ODR_26Hz;
419 }
420
421 else
422 {
423 odr_xl = val;
424 }
425
426 break;
427
428 case LSM6DSOX_ODR_PRGS_52Hz:
429 if (val == LSM6DSOX_XL_ODR_OFF)
430 {
431 odr_xl = LSM6DSOX_XL_ODR_52Hz;
432 }
433
434 else if (val == LSM6DSOX_XL_ODR_12Hz5)
435 {
436 odr_xl = LSM6DSOX_XL_ODR_52Hz;
437 }
438
439 else if (val == LSM6DSOX_XL_ODR_26Hz)
440 {
441 odr_xl = LSM6DSOX_XL_ODR_52Hz;
442 }
443
444 else
445 {
446 odr_xl = val;
447 }
448
449 break;
450
451 case LSM6DSOX_ODR_PRGS_104Hz:
452 if (val == LSM6DSOX_XL_ODR_OFF)
453 {
454 odr_xl = LSM6DSOX_XL_ODR_104Hz;
455 }
456
457 else if (val == LSM6DSOX_XL_ODR_12Hz5)
458 {
459 odr_xl = LSM6DSOX_XL_ODR_104Hz;
460 }
461
462 else if (val == LSM6DSOX_XL_ODR_26Hz)
463 {
464 odr_xl = LSM6DSOX_XL_ODR_104Hz;
465 }
466
467 else if (val == LSM6DSOX_XL_ODR_52Hz)
468 {
469 odr_xl = LSM6DSOX_XL_ODR_104Hz;
470 }
471
472 else
473 {
474 odr_xl = val;
475 }
476
477 break;
478
479 default:
480 odr_xl = val;
481 break;
482 }
483 }
484 }
485 }
486
487 if (ret == 0)
488 {
489 ret = lsm6dsox_read_reg(ctx, LSM6DSOX_CTRL1_XL, (uint8_t *)&reg, 1);
490 }
491
492 if (ret == 0)
493 {
494 reg.odr_xl = (uint8_t) odr_xl;
495 ret = lsm6dsox_write_reg(ctx, LSM6DSOX_CTRL1_XL, (uint8_t *)&reg, 1);
496 }
497
498 return ret;

910int32_t lsm6dsox_gy_data_rate_get(stmdev_ctx_t *ctx,

914 int32_t ret;
915
916 ret = lsm6dsox_read_reg(ctx, LSM6DSOX_CTRL2_G, (uint8_t *)&reg, 1);
917
918 switch (reg.odr_g)
919 {
920 case LSM6DSOX_GY_ODR_OFF:
921 *val = LSM6DSOX_GY_ODR_OFF;
922 break;
923
924 case LSM6DSOX_GY_ODR_12Hz5:
925 *val = LSM6DSOX_GY_ODR_12Hz5;
926 break;
927
928 case LSM6DSOX_GY_ODR_26Hz:
929 *val = LSM6DSOX_GY_ODR_26Hz;
930 break;
931
932 case LSM6DSOX_GY_ODR_52Hz:
933 *val = LSM6DSOX_GY_ODR_52Hz;
934 break;
935
936 case LSM6DSOX_GY_ODR_104Hz:
937 *val = LSM6DSOX_GY_ODR_104Hz;
938 break;
939
940 case LSM6DSOX_GY_ODR_208Hz:
941 *val = LSM6DSOX_GY_ODR_208Hz;
942 break;
943
944 case LSM6DSOX_GY_ODR_417Hz:
945 *val = LSM6DSOX_GY_ODR_417Hz;
946 break;
947
948 case LSM6DSOX_GY_ODR_833Hz:
949 *val = LSM6DSOX_GY_ODR_833Hz;
950 break;
951
952 case LSM6DSOX_GY_ODR_1667Hz:
953 *val = LSM6DSOX_GY_ODR_1667Hz;
954 break;
955
956 case LSM6DSOX_GY_ODR_3333Hz:
957 *val = LSM6DSOX_GY_ODR_3333Hz;
958 break;
959
960 case LSM6DSOX_GY_ODR_6667Hz:
961 *val = LSM6DSOX_GY_ODR_6667Hz;
962 break;
963
964 default:
965 *val = LSM6DSOX_GY_ODR_OFF;
966 break;
967 }
968
969 return ret;
970}

1086int32_t lsm6dsox_xl_power_mode_set(stmdev_ctx_t *ctx,
1087 lsm6dsox_xl_hm_mode_t val)
1088{
1089 lsm6dsox_ctrl5_c_t ctrl5_c;
1090 lsm6dsox_ctrl6_c_t ctrl6_c;
1091 int32_t ret;
1092
1093 ret = lsm6dsox_read_reg(ctx, LSM6DSOX_CTRL5_C, (uint8_t *) &ctrl5_c, 1);
1094
1095 if (ret == 0)
1096 {
1097 ctrl5_c.xl_ulp_en = ((uint8_t)val & 0x02U) >> 1;
1098 ret = lsm6dsox_write_reg(ctx, LSM6DSOX_CTRL5_C, (uint8_t *) &ctrl5_c, 1);
1099 }
1100
1101 if (ret == 0)
1102 {
1103 ret = lsm6dsox_read_reg(ctx, LSM6DSOX_CTRL6_C, (uint8_t *) &ctrl6_c, 1);
1104 }
1105
1106 if (ret == 0)
1107 {
1108 ctrl6_c.xl_hm_mode = (uint8_t)val & 0x01U;
1109 ret = lsm6dsox_write_reg(ctx, LSM6DSOX_CTRL6_C, (uint8_t *) &ctrl6_c, 1);
1110 }
1111
1112 return ret;
1113}
1114
1123int32_t lsm6dsox_xl_power_mode_get(stmdev_ctx_t *ctx,
1124 lsm6dsox_xl_hm_mode_t *val)
1125{
1126 lsm6dsox_ctrl5_c_t ctrl5_c;
1127 lsm6dsox_ctrl6_c_t ctrl6_c;
1128 int32_t ret;
1129
1130 ret = lsm6dsox_read_reg(ctx, LSM6DSOX_CTRL5_C, (uint8_t *) &ctrl5_c, 1);
1131
1132 if (ret == 0)
1133 {
1134 ret = lsm6dsox_read_reg(ctx, LSM6DSOX_CTRL6_C, (uint8_t *) &ctrl6_c, 1);
1135
1136 switch ((ctrl5_c.xl_ulp_en << 1) | ctrl6_c.xl_hm_mode)
1137 {
1138 case LSM6DSOX_HIGH_PERFORMANCE_MD:
1139 *val = LSM6DSOX_HIGH_PERFORMANCE_MD;
1140 break;
1141
1142 case LSM6DSOX_LOW_NORMAL_POWER_MD:
1143 *val = LSM6DSOX_LOW_NORMAL_POWER_MD;
1144 break;
1145
1146 case LSM6DSOX_ULTRA_LOW_POWER_MD:
1147 *val = LSM6DSOX_ULTRA_LOW_POWER_MD;
1148 break;
1149
1150 default:
1151 *val = LSM6DSOX_HIGH_PERFORMANCE_MD;
1152 break;
1153 }
1154 }
1155
1156 return ret;
1157}

1890 val[0] = (int16_t)buff[1];
1891 val[0] = (val[0] * 256) + (int16_t)buff[0];
1892 val[1] = (int16_t)buff[3];
1893 val[1] = (val[1] * 256) + (int16_t)buff[2];
1894 val[2] = (int16_t)buff[5];
1895 val[2] = (val[2] * 256) + (int16_t)buff[4];
1896
1897 return ret;
1898}

1914 uint8_t buff[6];
1915 int32_t ret;
1916

1920 val[1] = (int16_t)buff[3];
1921 val[1] = (val[1] * 256) + (int16_t)buff[2];

1925 return ret;

1936int32_t lsm6dsox_number_of_steps_get(stmdev_ctx_t *ctx, uint16_t *val)
1937{
1938 uint8_t buff[2];
1939 int32_t ret;
1940
1941 ret = lsm6dsox_mem_bank_set(ctx, LSM6DSOX_EMBEDDED_FUNC_BANK);
1942
1943 if (ret == 0)
1944 {
1945 ret = lsm6dsox_read_reg(ctx, LSM6DSOX_STEP_COUNTER_L, buff, 2);
1946 *val = buff[1];
1947 *val = (*val * 256U) + buff[0];
1948 }
1949
1950 if (ret == 0)
1951 {
1952 ret = lsm6dsox_mem_bank_set(ctx, LSM6DSOX_USER_BANK);
1953 }
1954
1955 return ret;
1956}

1965int32_t lsm6dsox_steps_reset(stmdev_ctx_t *ctx)
1966{
1967 lsm6dsox_emb_func_src_t reg;
1968 int32_t ret;
1969
1970 ret = lsm6dsox_mem_bank_set(ctx, LSM6DSOX_EMBEDDED_FUNC_BANK);
1971
1972 if (ret == 0)
1973 {
1974 ret = lsm6dsox_read_reg(ctx, LSM6DSOX_EMB_FUNC_SRC, (uint8_t *)&reg, 1);
1975 }
1976
1977 if (ret == 0)
1978 {
1979 reg.pedo_rst_step = PROPERTY_ENABLE;
1980 ret = lsm6dsox_write_reg(ctx, LSM6DSOX_EMB_FUNC_SRC, (uint8_t *)&reg, 1);
1981 }
1982
1983 if (ret == 0)
1984 {
1985 ret = lsm6dsox_mem_bank_set(ctx, LSM6DSOX_USER_BANK);
1986 }
1987
1988 return ret;
1989}

2121int32_t lsm6dsox_mem_bank_get(stmdev_ctx_t *ctx,
2122 lsm6dsox_reg_access_t *val)
2123{
2124 lsm6dsox_func_cfg_access_t reg;
2125 int32_t ret;
2126
2127 ret = lsm6dsox_read_reg(ctx, LSM6DSOX_FUNC_CFG_ACCESS,
2128 (uint8_t *)&reg, 1);
2129
2130 switch (reg.reg_access)
2131 {
2132 case LSM6DSOX_USER_BANK:
2133 *val = LSM6DSOX_USER_BANK;
2134 break;
2135
2136 case LSM6DSOX_SENSOR_HUB_BANK:
2137 *val = LSM6DSOX_SENSOR_HUB_BANK;
2138 break;
2139
2140 case LSM6DSOX_EMBEDDED_FUNC_BANK:
2141 *val = LSM6DSOX_EMBEDDED_FUNC_BANK;
2142 break;
2143
2144 default:
2145 *val = LSM6DSOX_USER_BANK;
2146 break;
2147 }
2148
2149 return ret;
2150}
2151
2161int32_t lsm6dsox_ln_pg_write_byte(stmdev_ctx_t *ctx, uint16_t address,
2162 uint8_t *val)
2163{
2164 lsm6dsox_page_rw_t page_rw;
2165 lsm6dsox_page_sel_t page_sel;
2166 lsm6dsox_page_address_t page_address;
2167 int32_t ret;
2168
2169 ret = lsm6dsox_mem_bank_set(ctx, LSM6DSOX_EMBEDDED_FUNC_BANK);
2170
2171 if (ret == 0)
2172 {
2173 ret = lsm6dsox_read_reg(ctx, LSM6DSOX_PAGE_RW, (uint8_t *) &page_rw, 1);
2174 }
2175
2176 if (ret == 0)
2177 {
2178 page_rw.page_rw = 0x02; /* page_write enable */
2179 ret = lsm6dsox_write_reg(ctx, LSM6DSOX_PAGE_RW, (uint8_t *) &page_rw, 1);
2180 }
2181
2182 if (ret == 0)
2183 {
2184 ret = lsm6dsox_read_reg(ctx, LSM6DSOX_PAGE_SEL, (uint8_t *) &page_sel, 1);
2185 }
2186
2187 if (ret == 0)
2188 {
2189 page_sel.page_sel = ((uint8_t)(address >> 8) & 0x0FU);
2190 page_sel.not_used_01 = 1;
2191 ret = lsm6dsox_write_reg(ctx, LSM6DSOX_PAGE_SEL,
2192 (uint8_t *) &page_sel, 1);
2193 }
2194
2195 if (ret == 0)
2196 {
2197 page_address.page_addr = (uint8_t)address & 0xFFU;
2198 ret = lsm6dsox_write_reg(ctx, LSM6DSOX_PAGE_ADDRESS,
2199 (uint8_t *)&page_address, 1);
2200 }
2201
2202 if (ret == 0)
2203 {
2204 ret = lsm6dsox_write_reg(ctx, LSM6DSOX_PAGE_VALUE, val, 1);
2205 }
2206
2207 if (ret == 0)
2208 {
2209 ret = lsm6dsox_read_reg(ctx, LSM6DSOX_PAGE_RW, (uint8_t *) &page_rw, 1);
2210 }
2211
2212 if (ret == 0)
2213 {
2214 page_rw.page_rw = 0x00; /* page_write disable */
2215 ret = lsm6dsox_write_reg(ctx, LSM6DSOX_PAGE_RW, (uint8_t *) &page_rw, 1);
2216 }
2217
2218 if (ret == 0)
2219 {
2220 ret = lsm6dsox_mem_bank_set(ctx, LSM6DSOX_USER_BANK);
2221 }
2222
2223 return ret;
2224}
2225
2236int32_t lsm6dsox_ln_pg_write(stmdev_ctx_t *ctx, uint16_t address,
2237 uint8_t *buf, uint8_t len)
2238{
2239 lsm6dsox_page_rw_t page_rw;
2240 lsm6dsox_page_sel_t page_sel;
2241 lsm6dsox_page_address_t page_address;
2242 int32_t ret;
2243
2244 uint8_t msb, lsb;
2245 uint8_t i ;
2246 msb = ((uint8_t)(address >> 8) & 0x0FU);
2247 lsb = (uint8_t)address & 0xFFU;
2248 ret = lsm6dsox_mem_bank_set(ctx, LSM6DSOX_EMBEDDED_FUNC_BANK);
2249
2250 if (ret == 0)
2251 {
2252 ret = lsm6dsox_read_reg(ctx, LSM6DSOX_PAGE_RW, (uint8_t *) &page_rw, 1);
2253 }
2254
2255 if (ret == 0)
2256 {
2257 page_rw.page_rw = 0x02; /* page_write enable*/
2258 ret = lsm6dsox_write_reg(ctx, LSM6DSOX_PAGE_RW, (uint8_t *) &page_rw, 1);
2259 }
2260
2261 if (ret == 0)
2262 {
2263 ret = lsm6dsox_read_reg(ctx, LSM6DSOX_PAGE_SEL, (uint8_t *) &page_sel, 1);
2264 }
2265
2266 if (ret == 0)
2267 {
2268 page_sel.page_sel = msb;
2269 page_sel.not_used_01 = 1;
2270 ret = lsm6dsox_write_reg(ctx, LSM6DSOX_PAGE_SEL,
2271 (uint8_t *) &page_sel, 1);
2272 }
2273
2274 if (ret == 0)
2275 {
2276 page_address.page_addr = lsb;
2277 ret = lsm6dsox_write_reg(ctx, LSM6DSOX_PAGE_ADDRESS,
2278 (uint8_t *)&page_address, 1);
2279 }
2280
2281 if (ret == 0)
2282 {
2283 for (i = 0; ((i < len) && (ret == 0)); i++)
2284 {
2285 ret = lsm6dsox_write_reg(ctx, LSM6DSOX_PAGE_VALUE, &buf[i], 1);
2286 lsb++;
2287
2288 /* Check if page wrap */
2289 if ((lsb == 0x00U) && (ret == 0))
2290 {
2291 msb++;
2292 ret = lsm6dsox_read_reg(ctx, LSM6DSOX_PAGE_SEL, (uint8_t *)&page_sel, 1);
2293
2294 if (ret == 0)
2295 {
2296 page_sel.page_sel = msb;
2297 page_sel.not_used_01 = 1;
2298 ret = lsm6dsox_write_reg(ctx, LSM6DSOX_PAGE_SEL,
2299 (uint8_t *)&page_sel, 1);
2300 }
2301 }
2302 }
2303 }
2304
2305 page_sel.page_sel = 0;
2306 page_sel.not_used_01 = 1;
2307 ret = lsm6dsox_write_reg(ctx, LSM6DSOX_PAGE_SEL,
2308 (uint8_t *) &page_sel, 1);
2309
2310 if (ret == 0)
2311 {
2312 ret = lsm6dsox_read_reg(ctx, LSM6DSOX_PAGE_RW, (uint8_t *) &page_rw, 1);
2313 }
2314
2315 if (ret == 0)
2316 {
2317 page_rw.page_rw = 0x00; /* page_write disable */
2318 ret = lsm6dsox_write_reg(ctx, LSM6DSOX_PAGE_RW, (uint8_t *) &page_rw, 1);
2319 }
2320
2321 if (ret == 0)
2322 {
2323 ret = lsm6dsox_mem_bank_set(ctx, LSM6DSOX_USER_BANK);
2324 }
2325
2326 return ret;
2327}
2328
2338int32_t lsm6dsox_ln_pg_read_byte(stmdev_ctx_t *ctx, uint16_t address,
2339 uint8_t *val)
2340{
2341 lsm6dsox_page_rw_t page_rw;
2342 lsm6dsox_page_sel_t page_sel;
2343 lsm6dsox_page_address_t page_address;
2344 int32_t ret;
2345
2346 ret = lsm6dsox_mem_bank_set(ctx, LSM6DSOX_EMBEDDED_FUNC_BANK);
2347
2348 if (ret == 0)
2349 {
2350 ret = lsm6dsox_read_reg(ctx, LSM6DSOX_PAGE_RW, (uint8_t *) &page_rw, 1);
2351 }
2352
2353 if (ret == 0)
2354 {
2355 page_rw.page_rw = 0x01; /* page_read enable*/
2356 ret = lsm6dsox_write_reg(ctx, LSM6DSOX_PAGE_RW, (uint8_t *) &page_rw, 1);
2357 }
2358
2359 if (ret == 0)
2360 {
2361 ret = lsm6dsox_read_reg(ctx, LSM6DSOX_PAGE_SEL, (uint8_t *) &page_sel, 1);
2362 }
2363
2364 if (ret == 0)
2365 {
2366 page_sel.page_sel = ((uint8_t)(address >> 8) & 0x0FU);
2367 page_sel.not_used_01 = 1;
2368 ret = lsm6dsox_write_reg(ctx, LSM6DSOX_PAGE_SEL,
2369 (uint8_t *) &page_sel, 1);
2370 }
2371
2372 if (ret == 0)
2373 {
2374 page_address.page_addr = (uint8_t)address & 0x00FFU;
2375 ret = lsm6dsox_write_reg(ctx, LSM6DSOX_PAGE_ADDRESS,
2376 (uint8_t *)&page_address, 1);
2377 }
2378
2379 if (ret == 0)
2380 {
2381 ret = lsm6dsox_read_reg(ctx, LSM6DSOX_PAGE_VALUE, val, 1);
2382 }
2383
2384 if (ret == 0)
2385 {
2386 ret = lsm6dsox_read_reg(ctx, LSM6DSOX_PAGE_RW, (uint8_t *) &page_rw, 1);
2387 }
2388
2389 if (ret == 0)
2390 {
2391 page_rw.page_rw = 0x00; /* page_read disable */
2392 ret = lsm6dsox_write_reg(ctx, LSM6DSOX_PAGE_RW, (uint8_t *) &page_rw, 1);
2393 }
2394
2395 if (ret == 0)
2396 {
2397 ret = lsm6dsox_mem_bank_set(ctx, LSM6DSOX_USER_BANK);
2398 }
2399
2400 return ret;
2401}

2714int32_t lsm6dsox_gy_self_test_get(stmdev_ctx_t *ctx,
2715 lsm6dsox_st_g_t *val)
2716{
2717 lsm6dsox_ctrl5_c_t reg;
2718 int32_t ret;
2719
2720 ret = lsm6dsox_read_reg(ctx, LSM6DSOX_CTRL5_C, (uint8_t *)&reg, 1);
2721
2722 switch (reg.st_g)
2723 {
2724 case LSM6DSOX_GY_ST_DISABLE:
2725 *val = LSM6DSOX_GY_ST_DISABLE;
2726 break;
2727
2728 case LSM6DSOX_GY_ST_POSITIVE:
2729 *val = LSM6DSOX_GY_ST_POSITIVE;
2730 break;
2731
2732 case LSM6DSOX_GY_ST_NEGATIVE:
2733 *val = LSM6DSOX_GY_ST_NEGATIVE;
2734 break;

3402 ret = lsm6dsox_write_reg(ctx, LSM6DSOX_FUNC_CFG_ACCESS,
3403 (uint8_t *)&func_cfg_access, 1);
3404 }

3803int32_t lsm6dsox_aux_den_mode_set(stmdev_ctx_t *ctx,
3804 lsm6dsox_lvl2_ois_t val)
3805{
3806 lsm6dsox_ui_ctrl1_ois_t ctrl1_ois;
3807 lsm6dsox_ui_int_ois_t int_ois;
3808 int32_t ret;
3809
3810 ret = lsm6dsox_read_reg(ctx, LSM6DSOX_UI_INT_OIS,
3811 (uint8_t *) &int_ois, 1);
3812
3813 if (ret == 0)
3814 {
3815 int_ois.lvl2_ois = (uint8_t)val & 0x01U;
3816 ret = lsm6dsox_write_reg(ctx, LSM6DSOX_UI_INT_OIS,
3817 (uint8_t *) &int_ois, 1);
3818 }
3819
3820 if (ret == 0)
3821 {
3822 ret = lsm6dsox_read_reg(ctx, LSM6DSOX_UI_CTRL1_OIS,
3823 (uint8_t *) &ctrl1_ois, 1);
3824 }
3825
3826 if (ret == 0)
3827 {
3828 ctrl1_ois.lvl1_ois = ((uint8_t)val & 0x02U) >> 1;
3829 ret = lsm6dsox_write_reg(ctx, LSM6DSOX_UI_CTRL1_OIS,
3830 (uint8_t *) &ctrl1_ois, 1);
3831 }
3832
3833 return ret;
3834}

3844int32_t lsm6dsox_aux_den_mode_get(stmdev_ctx_t *ctx,

3877 }

4695int32_t lsm6dsox_i3c_disable_set(stmdev_ctx_t *ctx,
4696 lsm6dsox_i3c_disable_t val)
4697{
4698 lsm6dsox_i3c_bus_avb_t i3c_bus_avb;
4699 lsm6dsox_ctrl9_xl_t ctrl9_xl;
4700 int32_t ret;
4701
4702 ret = lsm6dsox_read_reg(ctx, LSM6DSOX_CTRL9_XL, (uint8_t *)&ctrl9_xl, 1);
4703
4704 if (ret == 0)
4705 {
4706 ctrl9_xl.i3c_disable = ((uint8_t)val & 0x80U) >> 7;
4707 ret = lsm6dsox_write_reg(ctx, LSM6DSOX_CTRL9_XL, (uint8_t *)&ctrl9_xl, 1);
4708 }
4709
4710 if (ret == 0)
4711 {
4712 ret = lsm6dsox_read_reg(ctx, LSM6DSOX_I3C_BUS_AVB,
4713 (uint8_t *)&i3c_bus_avb, 1);
4714 }
4715
4716 if (ret == 0)
4717 {
4718 i3c_bus_avb.i3c_bus_avb_sel = (uint8_t)val & 0x03U;
4719 ret = lsm6dsox_write_reg(ctx, LSM6DSOX_I3C_BUS_AVB,
4720 (uint8_t *)&i3c_bus_avb, 1);
4721 }
4722
4723 return ret;
4724}
4725
4735int32_t lsm6dsox_i3c_disable_get(stmdev_ctx_t *ctx,
4736 lsm6dsox_i3c_disable_t *val)
4737{
4738 lsm6dsox_ctrl9_xl_t ctrl9_xl;
4739 lsm6dsox_i3c_bus_avb_t i3c_bus_avb;
4740 int32_t ret;
4741
4742 ret = lsm6dsox_read_reg(ctx, LSM6DSOX_CTRL9_XL, (uint8_t *)&ctrl9_xl, 1);
4743
4744 if (ret == 0)
4745 {
4746 ret = lsm6dsox_read_reg(ctx, LSM6DSOX_I3C_BUS_AVB,
4747 (uint8_t *)&i3c_bus_avb, 1);
4748
4749 switch ((ctrl9_xl.i3c_disable << 7) | i3c_bus_avb.i3c_bus_avb_sel)
4750 {
4751 case LSM6DSOX_I3C_DISABLE:
4752 *val = LSM6DSOX_I3C_DISABLE;
4753 break;
4754
4755 case LSM6DSOX_I3C_ENABLE_T_50us:
4756 *val = LSM6DSOX_I3C_ENABLE_T_50us;
4757 break;
4758
4759 case LSM6DSOX_I3C_ENABLE_T_2us:
4760 *val = LSM6DSOX_I3C_ENABLE_T_2us;
4761 break;
4762
4763 case LSM6DSOX_I3C_ENABLE_T_1ms:
4764 *val = LSM6DSOX_I3C_ENABLE_T_1ms;
4765 break;
4766
4767 case LSM6DSOX_I3C_ENABLE_T_25ms:
4768 *val = LSM6DSOX_I3C_ENABLE_T_25ms;
4769 break;
4770
4771 default:
4772 *val = LSM6DSOX_I3C_DISABLE;
4773 break;
4774 }
4775 }
4776
4777 return ret;
4778}

4800int32_t lsm6dsox_pin_mode_set(stmdev_ctx_t *ctx, lsm6dsox_pp_od_t val)
4801{
4802 lsm6dsox_i3c_bus_avb_t i3c_bus_avb;
4803 lsm6dsox_ctrl3_c_t ctrl3_c;
4804 int32_t ret;
4805
4806 ret = lsm6dsox_read_reg(ctx, LSM6DSOX_CTRL3_C, (uint8_t *)&ctrl3_c, 1);
4807
4808 if (ret == 0)
4809 {
4810 ctrl3_c.pp_od = (uint8_t)val;
4811 ret = lsm6dsox_write_reg(ctx, LSM6DSOX_CTRL3_C, (uint8_t *)&ctrl3_c, 1);
4812 }
4813
4814 if (ret == 0)
4815 {
4816 ret = lsm6dsox_read_reg(ctx, LSM6DSOX_I3C_BUS_AVB,
4817 (uint8_t *)&i3c_bus_avb, 1);
4818 }
4819
4820 if (ret == 0)
4821 {
4822 i3c_bus_avb.pd_dis_int1 = ((uint8_t) val & 0x02U) >> 1;
4823 ret = lsm6dsox_write_reg(ctx, LSM6DSOX_I3C_BUS_AVB,
4824 (uint8_t *)&i3c_bus_avb, 1);
4825 }
4826
4827 return ret;
4828}
4829
4838int32_t lsm6dsox_pin_mode_get(stmdev_ctx_t *ctx,
4839 lsm6dsox_pp_od_t *val)
4840{
4841 lsm6dsox_i3c_bus_avb_t i3c_bus_avb;
4842 lsm6dsox_ctrl3_c_t ctrl3_c;
4843 int32_t ret;
4844
4845 ret = lsm6dsox_read_reg(ctx, LSM6DSOX_CTRL3_C, (uint8_t *)&ctrl3_c, 1);
4846
4847 if (ret == 0)
4848 {
4849 ret = lsm6dsox_read_reg(ctx, LSM6DSOX_I3C_BUS_AVB,
4850 (uint8_t *)&i3c_bus_avb, 1);
4851 }
4852
4853 switch ((i3c_bus_avb.pd_dis_int1 << 1) + ctrl3_c.pp_od)
4854 {
4855 case LSM6DSOX_PUSH_PULL:
4856 *val = LSM6DSOX_PUSH_PULL;
4857 break;
4858
4859 case LSM6DSOX_OPEN_DRAIN:
4860 *val = LSM6DSOX_OPEN_DRAIN;
4861 break;
4862
4863 case LSM6DSOX_INT1_NOPULL_DOWN_INT2_PUSH_PULL:
4864 *val = LSM6DSOX_INT1_NOPULL_DOWN_INT2_PUSH_PULL;
4865 break;
4866
4867 case LSM6DSOX_INT1_NOPULL_DOWN_INT2_OPEN_DRAIN:
4868 *val = LSM6DSOX_INT1_NOPULL_DOWN_INT2_OPEN_DRAIN;
4869 break;
4870
4871 default:
4872 *val = LSM6DSOX_PUSH_PULL;
4873 break;
4874 }
4875
4876 return ret;
4877}

4989int32_t lsm6dsox_int_notification_set(stmdev_ctx_t *ctx,
4990 lsm6dsox_lir_t val)
4991{
4992 lsm6dsox_tap_cfg0_t tap_cfg0;
4993 lsm6dsox_page_rw_t page_rw;
4994 int32_t ret;
4995
4996 ret = lsm6dsox_read_reg(ctx, LSM6DSOX_TAP_CFG0, (uint8_t *) &tap_cfg0, 1);
4997
4998 if (ret == 0)
4999 {
5000 tap_cfg0.lir = (uint8_t)val & 0x01U;
5001 tap_cfg0.int_clr_on_read = (uint8_t)val & 0x01U;
5002 ret = lsm6dsox_write_reg(ctx, LSM6DSOX_TAP_CFG0,
5003 (uint8_t *) &tap_cfg0, 1);
5004 }
5005
5006 if (ret == 0)
5007 {
5008 ret = lsm6dsox_mem_bank_set(ctx, LSM6DSOX_EMBEDDED_FUNC_BANK);
5009 }
5010
5011 if (ret == 0)
5012 {
5013 ret = lsm6dsox_read_reg(ctx, LSM6DSOX_PAGE_RW, (uint8_t *) &page_rw, 1);
5014 }
5015
5016 if (ret == 0)
5017 {
5018 page_rw.emb_func_lir = ((uint8_t)val & 0x02U) >> 1;
5019 ret = lsm6dsox_write_reg(ctx, LSM6DSOX_PAGE_RW, (uint8_t *) &page_rw, 1);
5020 }
5021
5022 if (ret == 0)
5023 {
5024 ret = lsm6dsox_mem_bank_set(ctx, LSM6DSOX_USER_BANK);
5025 }
5026
5027 return ret;
5028}
5029
5038int32_t lsm6dsox_int_notification_get(stmdev_ctx_t *ctx,
5039 lsm6dsox_lir_t *val)
5040{
5041 lsm6dsox_tap_cfg0_t tap_cfg0;
5042 lsm6dsox_page_rw_t page_rw;
5043 int32_t ret;
5044
5045 ret = lsm6dsox_read_reg(ctx, LSM6DSOX_TAP_CFG0, (uint8_t *) &tap_cfg0, 1);
5046
5047 if (ret == 0)
5048 {
5049 ret = lsm6dsox_mem_bank_set(ctx, LSM6DSOX_EMBEDDED_FUNC_BANK);
5050 }
5051
5052 if (ret == 0)
5053 {
5054 ret = lsm6dsox_read_reg(ctx, LSM6DSOX_PAGE_RW, (uint8_t *) &page_rw, 1);
5055 }
5056
5057 if (ret == 0)
5058 {
5059 ret = lsm6dsox_mem_bank_set(ctx, LSM6DSOX_USER_BANK);
5060 }
5061
5062 if (ret == 0)
5063 {
5064 switch ((page_rw.emb_func_lir << 1) | tap_cfg0.lir)
5065 {
5066 case LSM6DSOX_ALL_INT_PULSED:
5067 *val = LSM6DSOX_ALL_INT_PULSED;
5068 break;
5069
5070 case LSM6DSOX_BASE_LATCHED_EMB_PULSED:
5071 *val = LSM6DSOX_BASE_LATCHED_EMB_PULSED;
5072 break;
5073
5074 case LSM6DSOX_BASE_PULSED_EMB_LATCHED:
5075 *val = LSM6DSOX_BASE_PULSED_EMB_LATCHED;
5076 break;
5077
5078 case LSM6DSOX_ALL_INT_LATCHED:
5079 *val = LSM6DSOX_ALL_INT_LATCHED;
5080 break;
5081
5082 default:
5083 *val = LSM6DSOX_ALL_INT_PULSED;
5084 break;
5085 }
5086
5087 ret = lsm6dsox_mem_bank_set(ctx, LSM6DSOX_EMBEDDED_FUNC_BANK);
5088 }
5089
5090 if (ret == 0)
5091 {
5092 ret = lsm6dsox_read_reg(ctx, LSM6DSOX_PAGE_RW, (uint8_t *) &page_rw, 1);
5093 }
5094
5095 if (ret == 0)
5096 {
5097 ret = lsm6dsox_mem_bank_set(ctx, LSM6DSOX_USER_BANK);
5098 }
5099
5100 return ret;
5101}

5339int32_t lsm6dsox_gy_sleep_mode_set(stmdev_ctx_t *ctx, uint8_t val)

5345

6326
6327 case LSM6DSOX_FF_TSH_406mg:
6328 *val = LSM6DSOX_FF_TSH_406mg;
6329 break;
6330
6331 case LSM6DSOX_FF_TSH_469mg:
6332 *val = LSM6DSOX_FF_TSH_469mg;
6333 break;
6334
6335 case LSM6DSOX_FF_TSH_500mg:
6336 *val = LSM6DSOX_FF_TSH_500mg;
6337 break;
6338
6339 default:
6340 *val = LSM6DSOX_FF_TSH_156mg;
6341 break;
6342 }
6343
6344 return ret;
6345}
6346
6356int32_t lsm6dsox_ff_dur_set(stmdev_ctx_t *ctx, uint8_t val)
6357{
6358 lsm6dsox_wake_up_dur_t wake_up_dur;
6359 lsm6dsox_free_fall_t free_fall;
6360 int32_t ret;
6361
6362 ret = lsm6dsox_read_reg(ctx, LSM6DSOX_WAKE_UP_DUR,
6363 (uint8_t *)&wake_up_dur, 1);
6364
6365 if (ret == 0)
6366 {
6367 ret = lsm6dsox_read_reg(ctx, LSM6DSOX_FREE_FALL,
6368 (uint8_t *)&free_fall, 1);
6369 }
6370
6371 if (ret == 0)
6372 {
6373 wake_up_dur.ff_dur = ((uint8_t)val & 0x20U) >> 5;
6374 free_fall.ff_dur = (uint8_t)val & 0x1FU;
6375 ret = lsm6dsox_write_reg(ctx, LSM6DSOX_WAKE_UP_DUR,
6376 (uint8_t *)&wake_up_dur, 1);
6377 }
6378
6379 if (ret == 0)
6380 {
6381 ret = lsm6dsox_write_reg(ctx, LSM6DSOX_FREE_FALL,
6382 (uint8_t *)&free_fall, 1);
6383 }
6384
6385 return ret;
6386}
6387
6397int32_t lsm6dsox_ff_dur_get(stmdev_ctx_t *ctx, uint8_t *val)
6398{
6399 lsm6dsox_wake_up_dur_t wake_up_dur;
6400 lsm6dsox_free_fall_t free_fall;
6401 int32_t ret;
6402
6403 ret = lsm6dsox_read_reg(ctx, LSM6DSOX_WAKE_UP_DUR,
6404 (uint8_t *)&wake_up_dur, 1);
6405
6406 if (ret == 0)
6407 {
6408 ret = lsm6dsox_read_reg(ctx, LSM6DSOX_FREE_FALL,
6409 (uint8_t *)&free_fall, 1);
6410 *val = (wake_up_dur.ff_dur << 5) + free_fall.ff_dur;
6411 }
6412
6413 return ret;
6414}
6415
6436int32_t lsm6dsox_fifo_watermark_set(stmdev_ctx_t *ctx, uint16_t val)
6437{
6438 lsm6dsox_fifo_ctrl1_t fifo_ctrl1;
6439 lsm6dsox_fifo_ctrl2_t fifo_ctrl2;
6440 int32_t ret;
6441
6442 ret = lsm6dsox_read_reg(ctx, LSM6DSOX_FIFO_CTRL2,
6443 (uint8_t *)&fifo_ctrl2, 1);
6444
6445 if (ret == 0)
6446 {
6447 fifo_ctrl1.wtm = 0x00FFU & (uint8_t)val;
6448 fifo_ctrl2.wtm = (uint8_t)((0x0100U & val) >> 8);
6449 ret = lsm6dsox_write_reg(ctx, LSM6DSOX_FIFO_CTRL1,
6450 (uint8_t *)&fifo_ctrl1, 1);
6451 }
6452
6453 if (ret == 0)
6454 {
6455 ret = lsm6dsox_write_reg(ctx, LSM6DSOX_FIFO_CTRL2,
6456 (uint8_t *)&fifo_ctrl2, 1);
6457 }
6458
6459 return ret;
6460}
6461
6470int32_t lsm6dsox_fifo_watermark_get(stmdev_ctx_t *ctx, uint16_t *val)
6471{
6472 lsm6dsox_fifo_ctrl1_t fifo_ctrl1;
6473 lsm6dsox_fifo_ctrl2_t fifo_ctrl2;
6474 int32_t ret;
6475
6476 ret = lsm6dsox_read_reg(ctx, LSM6DSOX_FIFO_CTRL1,
6477 (uint8_t *)&fifo_ctrl1, 1);
6478
6479 if (ret == 0)
6480 {
6481 ret = lsm6dsox_read_reg(ctx, LSM6DSOX_FIFO_CTRL2,
6482 (uint8_t *)&fifo_ctrl2, 1);
6483 *val = ((uint16_t)fifo_ctrl2.wtm << 8) + (uint16_t)fifo_ctrl1.wtm;
6484 }
6485
6486 return ret;
6487}

6498int32_t lsm6dsox_compression_algo_init_set(stmdev_ctx_t *ctx,
6499 uint8_t val)
6500{
6501 lsm6dsox_emb_func_init_b_t reg;
6502 int32_t ret;
6503
6504 ret = lsm6dsox_mem_bank_set(ctx, LSM6DSOX_EMBEDDED_FUNC_BANK);
6505
6506 if (ret == 0)
6507 {
6508 ret = lsm6dsox_read_reg(ctx, LSM6DSOX_EMB_FUNC_INIT_B,
6509 (uint8_t *)&reg, 1);
6510 }
6511
6512 if (ret == 0)
6513 {
6514 reg.fifo_compr_init = val;
6515 ret = lsm6dsox_write_reg(ctx, LSM6DSOX_EMB_FUNC_INIT_B,
6516 (uint8_t *)&reg, 1);
6517 }
6518
6519 if (ret == 0)
6520 {
6521 ret = lsm6dsox_mem_bank_set(ctx, LSM6DSOX_USER_BANK);
6522 }
6523
6524 return ret;
6525}

6568int32_t lsm6dsox_compression_algo_set(stmdev_ctx_t *ctx,
6569 lsm6dsox_uncoptr_rate_t val)
6570{
6571 lsm6dsox_fifo_ctrl2_t fifo_ctrl2;
6572 int32_t ret;
6573
6574 ret = lsm6dsox_read_reg(ctx, LSM6DSOX_FIFO_CTRL2,
6575 (uint8_t *)&fifo_ctrl2, 1);
6576
6577 if (ret == 0)
6578 {
6579 fifo_ctrl2.fifo_compr_rt_en = ((uint8_t)val & 0x04U) >> 2;
6580 fifo_ctrl2.uncoptr_rate = (uint8_t)val & 0x03U;
6581 ret = lsm6dsox_write_reg(ctx, LSM6DSOX_FIFO_CTRL2,
6582 (uint8_t *)&fifo_ctrl2, 1);
6583 }
6584
6585 return ret;
6586}
6587
6597int32_t lsm6dsox_compression_algo_get(stmdev_ctx_t *ctx,
6598 lsm6dsox_uncoptr_rate_t *val)
6599{
6600 lsm6dsox_fifo_ctrl2_t reg;
6601 int32_t ret;
6602
6603 ret = lsm6dsox_read_reg(ctx, LSM6DSOX_FIFO_CTRL2, (uint8_t *)&reg, 1);
6604
6605 switch ((reg.fifo_compr_rt_en << 2) | reg.uncoptr_rate)
6606 {
6607 case LSM6DSOX_CMP_DISABLE:
6608 *val = LSM6DSOX_CMP_DISABLE;
6609 break;
6610
6611 case LSM6DSOX_CMP_ALWAYS:
6612 *val = LSM6DSOX_CMP_ALWAYS;
6613 break;
6614
6615 case LSM6DSOX_CMP_8_TO_1:
6616 *val = LSM6DSOX_CMP_8_TO_1;
6617 break;
6618
6619 case LSM6DSOX_CMP_16_TO_1:
6620 *val = LSM6DSOX_CMP_16_TO_1;
6621 break;
6622
6623 case LSM6DSOX_CMP_32_TO_1:
6624 *val = LSM6DSOX_CMP_32_TO_1;
6625 break;
6626
6627 default:
6628 *val = LSM6DSOX_CMP_DISABLE;
6629 break;
6630 }
6631
6632 return ret;
6633}

7314int32_t lsm6dsox_batch_counter_threshold_set(stmdev_ctx_t *ctx,
7315 uint16_t val)
7316{
7317 lsm6dsox_counter_bdr_reg1_t counter_bdr_reg1;
7318 lsm6dsox_counter_bdr_reg2_t counter_bdr_reg2;
7319 int32_t ret;
7320
7321 ret = lsm6dsox_read_reg(ctx, LSM6DSOX_COUNTER_BDR_REG1,
7322 (uint8_t *)&counter_bdr_reg1, 1);
7323
7324 if (ret == 0)
7325 {
7326 counter_bdr_reg2.cnt_bdr_th = 0x00FFU & (uint8_t)val;
7327 counter_bdr_reg1.cnt_bdr_th = (uint8_t)(0x0700U & val) >> 8;
7328 ret = lsm6dsox_write_reg(ctx, LSM6DSOX_COUNTER_BDR_REG1,
7329 (uint8_t *)&counter_bdr_reg1, 1);
7330 }
7331
7332 if (ret == 0)
7333 {
7334 ret = lsm6dsox_write_reg(ctx, LSM6DSOX_COUNTER_BDR_REG2,
7335 (uint8_t *)&counter_bdr_reg2, 1);
7336 }
7337
7338 return ret;
7339}
7340
7350int32_t lsm6dsox_batch_counter_threshold_get(stmdev_ctx_t *ctx,
7351 uint16_t *val)
7352{
7353 lsm6dsox_counter_bdr_reg1_t counter_bdr_reg1;
7354 lsm6dsox_counter_bdr_reg2_t counter_bdr_reg2;
7355 int32_t ret;
7356
7357 ret = lsm6dsox_read_reg(ctx, LSM6DSOX_COUNTER_BDR_REG1,
7358 (uint8_t *)&counter_bdr_reg1, 1);
7359
7360 if (ret == 0)
7361 {
7362 ret = lsm6dsox_read_reg(ctx, LSM6DSOX_COUNTER_BDR_REG2,
7363 (uint8_t *)&counter_bdr_reg2, 1);
7364 *val = ((uint16_t)counter_bdr_reg1.cnt_bdr_th << 8)
7365 + (uint16_t)counter_bdr_reg2.cnt_bdr_th;
7366 }
7367
7368 return ret;
7369}

7380{

7956
7965int32_t lsm6dsox_den_mode_get(stmdev_ctx_t *ctx,
7966 lsm6dsox_den_mode_t *val)
7967{
7968 lsm6dsox_ctrl6_c_t reg;
7969 int32_t ret;
7970
7971 ret = lsm6dsox_read_reg(ctx, LSM6DSOX_CTRL6_C, (uint8_t *)&reg, 1);
7972
7973 switch (reg.den_mode)
7974 {
7975 case LSM6DSOX_DEN_DISABLE:
7976 *val = LSM6DSOX_DEN_DISABLE;
7977 break;
7978
7979 case LSM6DSOX_LEVEL_FIFO:
7980 *val = LSM6DSOX_LEVEL_FIFO;
7981 break;
7982
7983 case LSM6DSOX_LEVEL_LETCHED:
7984 *val = LSM6DSOX_LEVEL_LETCHED;
7985 break;
7986
7987 case LSM6DSOX_LEVEL_TRIGGER:
7988 *val = LSM6DSOX_LEVEL_TRIGGER;
7989 break;
7990
7991 case LSM6DSOX_EDGE_TRIGGER:
7992 *val = LSM6DSOX_EDGE_TRIGGER;
7993 break;
7994
7995 default:
7996 *val = LSM6DSOX_DEN_DISABLE;
7997 break;
7998 }
7999
8000 return ret;
8001}

8253
8274int32_t lsm6dsox_pedo_sens_set(stmdev_ctx_t *ctx,
8275 lsm6dsox_pedo_md_t val)
8276{
8277 lsm6dsox_pedo_cmd_reg_t pedo_cmd_reg;
8278 int32_t ret;
8279
8280 ret = lsm6dsox_ln_pg_read_byte(ctx, LSM6DSOX_PEDO_CMD_REG,
8281 (uint8_t *)&pedo_cmd_reg);
8282
8283 if (ret == 0)
8284 {
8285 pedo_cmd_reg.fp_rejection_en = ((uint8_t)val & 0x10U) >> 4;
8286 pedo_cmd_reg.ad_det_en = ((uint8_t)val & 0x20U) >> 5;
8287 ret = lsm6dsox_ln_pg_write_byte(ctx, LSM6DSOX_PEDO_CMD_REG,
8288 (uint8_t *)&pedo_cmd_reg);
8289 }
8290
8291 return ret;
8292}
8293
8302int32_t lsm6dsox_pedo_sens_get(stmdev_ctx_t *ctx,
8303 lsm6dsox_pedo_md_t *val)
8304{
8305 lsm6dsox_pedo_cmd_reg_t pedo_cmd_reg;
8306 int32_t ret;
8307
8308 ret = lsm6dsox_ln_pg_read_byte(ctx, LSM6DSOX_PEDO_CMD_REG,
8309 (uint8_t *)&pedo_cmd_reg);
8310
8311 switch ((pedo_cmd_reg.ad_det_en << 5) | (pedo_cmd_reg.fp_rejection_en
8312 << 4))
8313 {
8314 case LSM6DSOX_PEDO_BASE_MODE:
8315 *val = LSM6DSOX_PEDO_BASE_MODE;
8316 break;
8317
8318 case LSM6DSOX_FALSE_STEP_REJ:
8319 *val = LSM6DSOX_FALSE_STEP_REJ;
8320 break;
8321
8322 case LSM6DSOX_FALSE_STEP_REJ_ADV_MODE:
8323 *val = LSM6DSOX_FALSE_STEP_REJ_ADV_MODE;
8324 break;
8325
8326 default:
8327 *val = LSM6DSOX_PEDO_BASE_MODE;
8328 break;
8329 }
8330
8331 return ret;
8332}

8748int32_t lsm6dsox_mag_offset_set(stmdev_ctx_t *ctx, int16_t *val)
8749{
8750 uint8_t buff[6];
8751 int32_t ret;
8752
8753 uint8_t i;
8754 buff[1] = (uint8_t)((uint16_t)val[0] / 256U);
8755 buff[0] = (uint8_t)((uint16_t)val[0] - (buff[1] * 256U));
8756 buff[3] = (uint8_t)((uint16_t)val[1] / 256U);
8757 buff[2] = (uint8_t)((uint16_t)val[1] - (buff[3] * 256U));
8758 buff[5] = (uint8_t)((uint16_t)val[2] / 256U);
8759 buff[4] = (uint8_t)((uint16_t)val[2] - (buff[5] * 256U));
8760 i = 0x00U;
8761 ret = lsm6dsox_ln_pg_write_byte(ctx, LSM6DSOX_MAG_OFFX_L,
8762 &buff[i]);
8763
8764 if (ret == 0)
8765 {
8766 i++;
8767 ret = lsm6dsox_ln_pg_write_byte(ctx, LSM6DSOX_MAG_OFFX_H,
8768 &buff[i]);
8769 }
8770
8771 if (ret == 0)
8772 {
8773 i++;
8774 ret = lsm6dsox_ln_pg_write_byte(ctx, LSM6DSOX_MAG_OFFY_L,
8775 &buff[i]);
8776 }
8777
8778 if (ret == 0)
8779 {
8780 i++;
8781 ret = lsm6dsox_ln_pg_write_byte(ctx, LSM6DSOX_MAG_OFFY_H,
8782 &buff[i]);
8783 }
8784
8785 if (ret == 0)
8786 {
8787 i++;
8788 ret = lsm6dsox_ln_pg_write_byte(ctx, LSM6DSOX_MAG_OFFZ_L,
8789 &buff[i]);
8790 }
8791
8792 if (ret == 0)
8793 {
8794 i++;
8795 ret = lsm6dsox_ln_pg_write_byte(ctx, LSM6DSOX_MAG_OFFZ_H,
8796 &buff[i]);
8797 }
8798
8799 return ret;
8800}
8801
8810int32_t lsm6dsox_mag_offset_get(stmdev_ctx_t *ctx, int16_t *val)
8811{
8812 uint8_t buff[6];
8813 int32_t ret;
8814
8815 uint8_t i;
8816 i = 0x00U;
8817 ret = lsm6dsox_ln_pg_read_byte(ctx, LSM6DSOX_MAG_OFFX_L,
8818 &buff[i]);
8819
8820 if (ret == 0)
8821 {
8822 i++;
8823 ret = lsm6dsox_ln_pg_read_byte(ctx, LSM6DSOX_MAG_OFFX_H,
8824 &buff[i]);
8825 }
8826
8827 if (ret == 0)
8828 {
8829 i++;
8830 ret = lsm6dsox_ln_pg_read_byte(ctx, LSM6DSOX_MAG_OFFY_L,
8831 &buff[i]);
8832 }
8833
8834 if (ret == 0)
8835 {
8836 i++;
8837 ret = lsm6dsox_ln_pg_read_byte(ctx, LSM6DSOX_MAG_OFFY_H,
8838 &buff[i]);
8839 }
8840
8841 if (ret == 0)
8842 {
8843 i++;
8844 ret = lsm6dsox_ln_pg_read_byte(ctx, LSM6DSOX_MAG_OFFZ_L,
8845 &buff[i]);
8846 }
8847
8848 if (ret == 0)
8849 {
8850 i++;
8851 ret = lsm6dsox_ln_pg_read_byte(ctx, LSM6DSOX_MAG_OFFZ_H,
8852 &buff[i]);
8853 }
8854
8855 val[0] = (int16_t)buff[1];
8856 val[0] = (val[0] * 256) + (int16_t)buff[0];
8857 val[1] = (int16_t)buff[3];
8858 val[1] = (val[1] * 256) + (int16_t)buff[2];
8859 val[2] = (int16_t)buff[5];
8860 val[2] = (val[2] * 256) + (int16_t)buff[4];
8861
8862 return ret;
8863}
8864
8879int32_t lsm6dsox_mag_soft_iron_set(stmdev_ctx_t *ctx, uint16_t *val)
8880{
8881 uint8_t buff[12];
8882 uint8_t index;
8883 int32_t ret;
8884
8885 buff[1] = (uint8_t)(val[0] / 256U);
8886 buff[0] = (uint8_t)(val[0] - (buff[1] * 256U));
8887 buff[3] = (uint8_t)(val[1] / 256U);
8888 buff[2] = (uint8_t)(val[1] - (buff[3] * 256U));
8889 buff[5] = (uint8_t)(val[2] / 256U);
8890 buff[4] = (uint8_t)(val[2] - (buff[5] * 256U));
8891 buff[7] = (uint8_t)(val[3] / 256U);
8892 buff[6] = (uint8_t)(val[3] - (buff[1] * 256U));
8893 buff[9] = (uint8_t)(val[4] / 256U);
8894 buff[8] = (uint8_t)(val[4] - (buff[3] * 256U));
8895 buff[11] = (uint8_t)(val[5] / 256U);
8896 buff[10] = (uint8_t)(val[5] - (buff[5] * 256U));
8897 index = 0x00U;
8898 ret = lsm6dsox_ln_pg_write_byte(ctx, LSM6DSOX_MAG_SI_XX_L,
8899 &buff[index]);
8900
8901 if (ret == 0)
8902 {
8903 index++;

8996int32_t lsm6dsox_mag_soft_iron_get(stmdev_ctx_t *ctx, uint16_t *val)
8997{
8998 uint8_t buff[12];
8999 uint8_t index;
9000 int32_t ret;
9001
9002 index = 0x00U;
9003 ret = lsm6dsox_ln_pg_read_byte(ctx, LSM6DSOX_MAG_SI_XX_L,
9004 &buff[index]);
9005
9006 if (ret == 0)

9015 index++;
9016 ret = lsm6dsox_ln_pg_read_byte(ctx, LSM6DSOX_MAG_SI_XY_L,
9017 &buff[index]);
9018 }
9019
9020 if (ret == 0)
9021 {
9022 index++;
9023 ret = lsm6dsox_ln_pg_read_byte(ctx, LSM6DSOX_MAG_SI_XY_H,
9024 &buff[index]);
9025 }
9026
9027 if (ret == 0)
9028 {
9029 index++;
9030 ret = lsm6dsox_ln_pg_read_byte(ctx, LSM6DSOX_MAG_SI_XZ_L,
9031 &buff[index]);
9032 }
9033
9034 if (ret == 0)
9035 {
9036 index++;
9037 ret = lsm6dsox_ln_pg_read_byte(ctx, LSM6DSOX_MAG_SI_XZ_H,
9038 &buff[index]);
9039 }
9040
9041 if (ret == 0)
9042 {
9043 index++;
9044 ret = lsm6dsox_ln_pg_read_byte(ctx, LSM6DSOX_MAG_SI_YY_L,
9045 &buff[index]);
9046 }
9047
9048 if (ret == 0)
9049 {
9050 index++;
9051 ret = lsm6dsox_ln_pg_read_byte(ctx, LSM6DSOX_MAG_SI_YY_H,
9052 &buff[index]);
9053 }
9054
9055 if (ret == 0)
9056 {
9057 index++;
9058 ret = lsm6dsox_ln_pg_read_byte(ctx, LSM6DSOX_MAG_SI_YZ_L,
9059 &buff[index]);
9060 }
9061
9062 if (ret == 0)
9063 {
9064 index++;
9065 ret = lsm6dsox_ln_pg_read_byte(ctx, LSM6DSOX_MAG_SI_YZ_H,
9066 &buff[index]);
9067 }
9068
9069 if (ret == 0)
9070 {
9071 index++;
9072 ret = lsm6dsox_ln_pg_read_byte(ctx, LSM6DSOX_MAG_SI_ZZ_L,
9073 &buff[index]);
9074 }
9075
9076 if (ret == 0)
9077 {
9078 index++;
9079 ret = lsm6dsox_ln_pg_read_byte(ctx, LSM6DSOX_MAG_SI_ZZ_H,
9080 &buff[index]);
9081 }
9082
9083 val[0] = buff[1];
9084 val[0] = (val[0] * 256U) + buff[0];
9085 val[1] = buff[3];
9086 val[1] = (val[1] * 256U) + buff[2];
9087 val[2] = buff[5];
9088 val[2] = (val[2] * 256U) + buff[4];
9089 val[3] = buff[7];
9090 val[3] = (val[3] * 256U) + buff[6];
9091 val[4] = buff[9];
9092 val[4] = (val[4] * 256U) + buff[8];
9093 val[5] = buff[11];
9094 val[6] = (val[5] * 256U) + buff[10];
9095
9096 return ret;
9097}

9486 }

9764 }

9810int32_t lsm6dsox_long_cnt_int_value_set(stmdev_ctx_t *ctx,
9811 uint16_t val)
9812{
9813 int32_t ret;
9814
9815 uint8_t add_l;
9816 uint8_t add_h;
9817 add_h = (uint8_t)((val & 0xFF00U) >> 8);
9818 add_l = (uint8_t)(val & 0x00FFU);
9819 ret = lsm6dsox_ln_pg_write_byte(ctx, LSM6DSOX_FSM_LC_TIMEOUT_L,
9820 &add_l);
9821
9822 if (ret == 0)
9823 {
9824 ret = lsm6dsox_ln_pg_write_byte(ctx, LSM6DSOX_FSM_LC_TIMEOUT_H,
9825 &add_h);
9826 }
9827
9828 return ret;
9829}
9830
9842int32_t lsm6dsox_long_cnt_int_value_get(stmdev_ctx_t *ctx,
9843 uint16_t *val)
9844{
9845 int32_t ret;
9846
9847 uint8_t add_l;
9848 uint8_t add_h;
9849 ret = lsm6dsox_ln_pg_read_byte(ctx, LSM6DSOX_FSM_LC_TIMEOUT_L,
9850 &add_l);
9851
9852 if (ret == 0)
9853 {
9854 ret = lsm6dsox_ln_pg_read_byte(ctx, LSM6DSOX_FSM_LC_TIMEOUT_H,
9855 &add_h);
9856 *val = add_h;
9857 *val = *val << 8;
9858 *val += add_l;
9859 }
9860
9861 return ret;
9862}

10071 }

10652 lsm6dsox_shub_odr_t val)
10653{
10654 lsm6dsox_slv0_config_t reg;
10655 int32_t ret;
10656
10657 ret = lsm6dsox_mem_bank_set(ctx, LSM6DSOX_SENSOR_HUB_BANK);
10658
10659 if (ret == 0)
10660 {
10661 ret = lsm6dsox_read_reg(ctx, LSM6DSOX_SLV0_CONFIG, (uint8_t *)&reg, 1);
10662 }
10663
10664 if (ret == 0)
10665 {
10666 reg.shub_odr = (uint8_t)val;
10667 ret = lsm6dsox_write_reg(ctx, LSM6DSOX_SLV0_CONFIG, (uint8_t *)&reg, 1);
10668 }
10669
10670 if (ret == 0)
10671 {
10672 ret = lsm6dsox_mem_bank_set(ctx, LSM6DSOX_USER_BANK);
10673 }
10674
10675 return ret;
10676}
10677
10686int32_t lsm6dsox_sh_data_rate_get(stmdev_ctx_t *ctx,
10687 lsm6dsox_shub_odr_t *val)
10688{
10689 lsm6dsox_slv0_config_t reg;
10690 int32_t ret;
10691
10692 ret = lsm6dsox_mem_bank_set(ctx, LSM6DSOX_SENSOR_HUB_BANK);
10693
10694 if (ret == 0)
10695 {
10696 ret = lsm6dsox_read_reg(ctx, LSM6DSOX_SLV0_CONFIG, (uint8_t *)&reg, 1);
10697 }
10698
10699 if (ret == 0)
10700 {
10701 switch (reg.shub_odr)
10702 {
10703 case LSM6DSOX_SH_ODR_104Hz:
10704 *val = LSM6DSOX_SH_ODR_104Hz;
10705 break;
10706
10707 case LSM6DSOX_SH_ODR_52Hz:
10708 *val = LSM6DSOX_SH_ODR_52Hz;
10709 break;
10710
10711 case LSM6DSOX_SH_ODR_26Hz:
10712 *val = LSM6DSOX_SH_ODR_26Hz;
10713 break;
10714
10715 case LSM6DSOX_SH_ODR_13Hz:
10716 *val = LSM6DSOX_SH_ODR_13Hz;
10717 break;
10718
10719 default:
10720 *val = LSM6DSOX_SH_ODR_104Hz;
10721 break;
10722 }
10723
10724 ret = lsm6dsox_mem_bank_set(ctx, LSM6DSOX_USER_BANK);
10725 }
10726
10727 return ret;
10728}
10729
10741int32_t lsm6dsox_sh_cfg_write(stmdev_ctx_t *ctx,
10742 lsm6dsox_sh_cfg_write_t *val)
10743{
10744 lsm6dsox_slv0_add_t reg;
10745 int32_t ret;
10746
10747 ret = lsm6dsox_mem_bank_set(ctx, LSM6DSOX_SENSOR_HUB_BANK);
10748
10749 if (ret == 0)
10750 {
10751 reg.slave0 = val->slv0_add;
10752 reg.rw_0 = 0;
10753 ret = lsm6dsox_write_reg(ctx, LSM6DSOX_SLV0_ADD, (uint8_t *)&reg, 1);
10754 }
10755
10756 if (ret == 0)
10757 {
10758 ret = lsm6dsox_write_reg(ctx, LSM6DSOX_SLV0_SUBADD,
10759 &(val->slv0_subadd), 1);
10760 }
10761
10762 if (ret == 0)
10763 {
10764 ret = lsm6dsox_write_reg(ctx, LSM6DSOX_DATAWRITE_SLV0,
10765 &(val->slv0_data), 1);
10766 }
10767
10768 if (ret == 0)
10769 {
10770 ret = lsm6dsox_mem_bank_set(ctx, LSM6DSOX_USER_BANK);
10771 }
10772
10773 return ret;
10774}

10787int32_t lsm6dsox_sh_slv0_cfg_read(stmdev_ctx_t *ctx,
10788 lsm6dsox_sh_cfg_read_t *val)
10789{
10790 lsm6dsox_slv0_add_t slv0_add;
10791 lsm6dsox_slv0_config_t slv0_config;
10792 int32_t ret;
10793
10794 ret = lsm6dsox_mem_bank_set(ctx, LSM6DSOX_SENSOR_HUB_BANK);
10795
10796 if (ret == 0)
10797 {
10798 slv0_add.slave0 = val->slv_add;
10799 slv0_add.rw_0 = 1;
10800 ret = lsm6dsox_write_reg(ctx, LSM6DSOX_SLV0_ADD, (uint8_t *)&slv0_add, 1);
10801 }
10802
10803 if (ret == 0)
10804 {
10805 ret = lsm6dsox_write_reg(ctx, LSM6DSOX_SLV0_SUBADD,
10806 &(val->slv_subadd), 1);
10807 }
10808
10809 if (ret == 0)
10810 {
10811 ret = lsm6dsox_read_reg(ctx, LSM6DSOX_SLV0_CONFIG,
10812 (uint8_t *)&slv0_config, 1);
10813 }
10814
10815 if (ret == 0)
10816 {
10817 slv0_config.slave0_numop = val->slv_len;
10818 ret = lsm6dsox_write_reg(ctx, LSM6DSOX_SLV0_CONFIG,
10819 (uint8_t *)&slv0_config, 1);
10820 }
10821
10822 if (ret == 0)
10823 {
10824 ret = lsm6dsox_mem_bank_set(ctx, LSM6DSOX_USER_BANK);
10825 }
10826
10827 return ret;
10828}

11073

11086 break;

11101int32_t lsm6dsox_s4s_tph_val_set(stmdev_ctx_t *ctx, uint16_t val)
11102{
11103 lsm6dsox_s4s_tph_l_t s4s_tph_l;
11104 lsm6dsox_s4s_tph_h_t s4s_tph_h;
11105 int32_t ret;
11106
11107 ret = lsm6dsox_read_reg(ctx, LSM6DSOX_S4S_TPH_L,
11108 (uint8_t *)&s4s_tph_l, 1);
11109
11110 if (ret == 0)
11111 {
11112 s4s_tph_l.tph_l = (uint8_t)(val & 0x007FU);
11113 ret = lsm6dsox_write_reg(ctx, LSM6DSOX_S4S_TPH_L,
11114 (uint8_t *)&s4s_tph_l, 1);
11115 }
11116
11117 if (ret == 0)
11118 {
11119 ret = lsm6dsox_read_reg(ctx, LSM6DSOX_S4S_TPH_H,
11120 (uint8_t *)&s4s_tph_h, 1);
11121 s4s_tph_h.tph_h = (uint8_t)(val & 0x7F80U) >> 7;
11122 }
11123
11124 if (ret == 0)
11125 {
11126 ret = lsm6dsox_write_reg(ctx, LSM6DSOX_S4S_TPH_H,
11127 (uint8_t *)&s4s_tph_h, 1);
11128 }
11129
11130 return ret;
11131}
11132
11142int32_t lsm6dsox_s4s_tph_val_get(stmdev_ctx_t *ctx, uint16_t *val)
11143{
11144 lsm6dsox_s4s_tph_l_t s4s_tph_l;
11145 lsm6dsox_s4s_tph_h_t s4s_tph_h;
11146 int32_t ret;
11147
11148 ret = lsm6dsox_read_reg(ctx, LSM6DSOX_S4S_TPH_L,
11149 (uint8_t *)&s4s_tph_l, 1);
11150
11151 if (ret == 0)
11152 {
11153 ret = lsm6dsox_read_reg(ctx, LSM6DSOX_S4S_TPH_H,
11154 (uint8_t *)&s4s_tph_h, 1);
11155 *val = s4s_tph_h.tph_h;
11156 *val = *val << 7;
11157 *val += s4s_tph_l.tph_l;
11158 }
11159
11160 return ret;
11161}

11224 default:

11226 break;

11346int32_t lsm6dsox_id_get(stmdev_ctx_t *ctx, stmdev_ctx_t *aux_ctx,
11347 lsm6dsox_id_t *val)
11348{

11350
11351 if (ctx != NULL)
11352 {
11353 ret = lsm6dsox_read_reg(ctx, LSM6DSOX_WHO_AM_I,
11354 (uint8_t *) & (val->ui), 1);
11355 }
11356
11357 if (aux_ctx != NULL)
11358 {
11359 if (ret == 0)
11360 {
11361 ret = lsm6dsox_read_reg(aux_ctx, LSM6DSOX_SPI2_WHO_AM_I,
11362 (uint8_t *) & (val->aux), 1);
11363 }
11364 }
11365
11366 return ret;

11368
11380int32_t lsm6dsox_init_set(stmdev_ctx_t *ctx, lsm6dsox_init_t val)
11381{
11382 lsm6dsox_emb_func_init_a_t emb_func_init_a;
11383 lsm6dsox_emb_func_init_b_t emb_func_init_b;
11384 lsm6dsox_ctrl3_c_t ctrl3_c;
11385 int32_t ret;
11386
11387 ret = lsm6dsox_mem_bank_set(ctx, LSM6DSOX_EMBEDDED_FUNC_BANK);
11388
11389 if (ret == 0)
11390 {
11391 ret = lsm6dsox_read_reg(ctx, LSM6DSOX_EMB_FUNC_INIT_B,
11392 (uint8_t *)&emb_func_init_b, 1);
11393 }
11394
11395 if (ret == 0)
11396 {
11397 emb_func_init_b.fifo_compr_init = (uint8_t)val
11398 & ((uint8_t)LSM6DSOX_FIFO_COMP >> 2);
11399 emb_func_init_b.fsm_init = (uint8_t)val
11400 & ((uint8_t)LSM6DSOX_FSM >> 3);
11401 emb_func_init_b.mlc_init = (uint8_t)val
11402 & ((uint8_t)LSM6DSOX_MLC >> 4);
11403 ret = lsm6dsox_write_reg(ctx, LSM6DSOX_EMB_FUNC_INIT_B,
11404 (uint8_t *)&emb_func_init_b, 1);
11405 }
11406
11407 if (ret == 0)
11408 {
11409 ret = lsm6dsox_read_reg(ctx, LSM6DSOX_EMB_FUNC_INIT_A,
11410 (uint8_t *)&emb_func_init_a, 1);
11411 }
11412
11413 if (ret == 0)
11414 {
11415 emb_func_init_a.step_det_init = ((uint8_t)val
11416 & (uint8_t)LSM6DSOX_PEDO) >> 5;
11417 emb_func_init_a.tilt_init = ((uint8_t)val
11418 & (uint8_t)LSM6DSOX_TILT) >> 6;
11419 emb_func_init_a.sig_mot_init = ((uint8_t)val
11420 & (uint8_t)LSM6DSOX_SMOTION) >> 7;
11421 ret = lsm6dsox_write_reg(ctx, LSM6DSOX_EMB_FUNC_INIT_A,
11422 (uint8_t *)&emb_func_init_a, 1);
11423 }
11424
11425 if (ret == 0)
11426 {
11427 ret = lsm6dsox_mem_bank_set(ctx, LSM6DSOX_USER_BANK);
11428 }
11429
11430 if (ret == 0)
11431 {
11432 ret = lsm6dsox_read_reg(ctx, LSM6DSOX_CTRL3_C, (uint8_t *)&ctrl3_c, 1);
11433 }
11434
11435 if (((val == LSM6DSOX_BOOT) || (val == LSM6DSOX_RESET)) &&
11436 (ret == 0))
11437 {
11438 ctrl3_c.boot = (uint8_t)val & (uint8_t)LSM6DSOX_BOOT;
11439 ctrl3_c.sw_reset = ((uint8_t)val & (uint8_t)LSM6DSOX_RESET) >> 1;
11440 ret = lsm6dsox_write_reg(ctx, LSM6DSOX_CTRL3_C, (uint8_t *)&ctrl3_c, 1);
11441 }
11442
11443 if ((val == LSM6DSOX_DRV_RDY)
11444 && ((ctrl3_c.bdu == PROPERTY_DISABLE)
11445 || (ctrl3_c.if_inc == PROPERTY_DISABLE)) && (ret == 0))
11446 {
11447 ctrl3_c.bdu = PROPERTY_ENABLE;
11448 ctrl3_c.if_inc = PROPERTY_ENABLE;
11449 ret = lsm6dsox_write_reg(ctx, LSM6DSOX_CTRL3_C, (uint8_t *)&ctrl3_c, 1);
11450 }
11451
11452 return ret;
11453}
11454
11467int32_t lsm6dsox_bus_mode_set(stmdev_ctx_t *ctx,
11468 stmdev_ctx_t *aux_ctx,
11469 lsm6dsox_bus_mode_t val)
11470{
11471 lsm6dsox_spi2_ctrl1_ois_t spi2_ctrl1_ois;
11472 lsm6dsox_i3c_bus_avb_t i3c_bus_avb;
11473 lsm6dsox_ctrl9_xl_t ctrl9_xl;
11474 lsm6dsox_ctrl3_c_t ctrl3_c;
11475 lsm6dsox_ctrl4_c_t ctrl4_c;
11476 uint8_t bit_val;
11477 int32_t ret;
11478
11479 ret = 0;
11480
11481 if (aux_ctx != NULL)
11482 {
11483 ret = lsm6dsox_read_reg(aux_ctx, LSM6DSOX_SPI2_CTRL1_OIS,
11484 (uint8_t *)&spi2_ctrl1_ois, 1);
11485 bit_val = ((uint8_t)val.aux_bus_md & 0x04U) >> 2;
11486
11487 if ((ret == 0) && (spi2_ctrl1_ois.sim_ois != bit_val))
11488 {
11489 spi2_ctrl1_ois.sim_ois = bit_val;
11490 ret = lsm6dsox_write_reg(aux_ctx, LSM6DSOX_SPI2_CTRL1_OIS,
11491 (uint8_t *)&spi2_ctrl1_ois, 1);
11492 }
11493 }
11494
11495 if (ctx != NULL)
11496 {
11497 if (ret == 0)
11498 {
11499 ret = lsm6dsox_read_reg(ctx, LSM6DSOX_CTRL9_XL,
11500 (uint8_t *)&ctrl9_xl, 1);
11501 }
11502
11503 bit_val = ((uint8_t)val.ui_bus_md & 0x04U) >> 2;
11504
11505 if ((ret == 0) && (ctrl9_xl.i3c_disable != bit_val))
11506 {
11507 ctrl9_xl.i3c_disable = bit_val;
11508 ret = lsm6dsox_write_reg(ctx, LSM6DSOX_CTRL9_XL,
11509 (uint8_t *)&ctrl9_xl, 1);
11510 }
11511
11512 if (ret == 0)
11513 {
11514 ret = lsm6dsox_read_reg(ctx, LSM6DSOX_I3C_BUS_AVB,
11515 (uint8_t *)&i3c_bus_avb, 1);
11516 }
11517
11518 bit_val = ((uint8_t)val.ui_bus_md & 0x30U) >> 4;
11519
11520 if ((ret == 0) && (i3c_bus_avb.i3c_bus_avb_sel != bit_val))
11521 {
11522 i3c_bus_avb.i3c_bus_avb_sel = bit_val;
11523 ret = lsm6dsox_write_reg(ctx, LSM6DSOX_I3C_BUS_AVB,
11524 (uint8_t *)&i3c_bus_avb, 1);
11525 }
11526
11527 if (ret == 0)
11528 {
11529 ret = lsm6dsox_read_reg(ctx, LSM6DSOX_CTRL4_C,
11530 (uint8_t *)&ctrl4_c, 1);
11531 }
11532
11533 bit_val = ((uint8_t)val.ui_bus_md & 0x02U) >> 1;
11534
11535 if ((ret == 0) && (ctrl4_c.i2c_disable != bit_val))
11536 {
11537 ctrl4_c.i2c_disable = bit_val;
11538 ret = lsm6dsox_write_reg(ctx, LSM6DSOX_CTRL4_C,
11539 (uint8_t *)&ctrl4_c, 1);
11540 }
11541
11542 if (ret == 0)
11543 {
11544 ret = lsm6dsox_read_reg(ctx, LSM6DSOX_CTRL3_C,
11545 (uint8_t *)&ctrl3_c, 1);
11546 }
11547
11548 bit_val = (uint8_t)val.ui_bus_md & 0x01U;
11549
11550 if ((ret == 0) && (ctrl3_c.sim != bit_val))
11551 {
11552 ctrl3_c.sim = bit_val;
11553 ret = lsm6dsox_write_reg(ctx, LSM6DSOX_CTRL3_C,
11554 (uint8_t *)&ctrl3_c, 1);
11555 }
11556 }
11557
11558 return ret;
11559}
11560
11573int32_t lsm6dsox_bus_mode_get(stmdev_ctx_t *ctx,
11574 stmdev_ctx_t *aux_ctx,
11575 lsm6dsox_bus_mode_t *val)
11576{
11577 lsm6dsox_spi2_ctrl1_ois_t spi2_ctrl1_ois;
11578 lsm6dsox_i3c_bus_avb_t i3c_bus_avb;
11579 lsm6dsox_ctrl9_xl_t ctrl9_xl;
11580 lsm6dsox_ctrl3_c_t ctrl3_c;
11581 lsm6dsox_ctrl4_c_t ctrl4_c;
11582 int32_t ret = 0;
11583
11584 if (aux_ctx != NULL)
11585 {
11586 ret = lsm6dsox_read_reg(aux_ctx, LSM6DSOX_SPI2_CTRL1_OIS,
11587 (uint8_t *)&spi2_ctrl1_ois, 1);
11588
11589 switch (spi2_ctrl1_ois.sim_ois)
11590 {
11591 case LSM6DSOX_SPI_4W_AUX:
11592 val->aux_bus_md = LSM6DSOX_SPI_4W_AUX;
11593 break;
11594
11595 case LSM6DSOX_SPI_3W_AUX:
11596 val->aux_bus_md = LSM6DSOX_SPI_3W_AUX;
11597 break;
11598
11599 default:
11600 val->aux_bus_md = LSM6DSOX_SPI_4W_AUX;
11601 break;
11602 }
11603 }
11604
11605 if (ctx != NULL)
11606 {
11607 if (ret == 0)
11608 {
11609 ret = lsm6dsox_read_reg(ctx, LSM6DSOX_CTRL9_XL,
11610 (uint8_t *)&ctrl9_xl, 1);
11611 }
11612
11613 if (ret == 0)
11614 {
11615 ret = lsm6dsox_read_reg(ctx, LSM6DSOX_I3C_BUS_AVB,
11616 (uint8_t *)&i3c_bus_avb, 1);
11617 }
11618
11619 if (ret == 0)
11620 {
11621 ret = lsm6dsox_read_reg(ctx, LSM6DSOX_CTRL4_C,
11622 (uint8_t *)&ctrl4_c, 1);
11623 }
11624
11625 if (ret == 0)
11626 {
11627 ret = lsm6dsox_read_reg(ctx, LSM6DSOX_CTRL3_C,
11628 (uint8_t *)&ctrl3_c, 1);
11629
11630 switch ((i3c_bus_avb.i3c_bus_avb_sel << 4) &
11631 (ctrl9_xl.i3c_disable << 2) &
11632 (ctrl4_c.i2c_disable << 1) & ctrl3_c.sim)
11633 {
11634 case LSM6DSOX_SEL_BY_HW:
11635 val->ui_bus_md = LSM6DSOX_SEL_BY_HW;
11636 break;
11637
11638 case LSM6DSOX_SPI_4W:
11639 val->ui_bus_md = LSM6DSOX_SPI_4W;
11640 break;
11641
11642 case LSM6DSOX_SPI_3W:
11643 val->ui_bus_md = LSM6DSOX_SPI_3W;
11644 break;
11645
11646 case LSM6DSOX_I2C:
11647 val->ui_bus_md = LSM6DSOX_I2C;
11648 break;
11649
11650 case LSM6DSOX_I3C_T_50us:
11651 val->ui_bus_md = LSM6DSOX_I3C_T_50us;
11652 break;
11653
11654 case LSM6DSOX_I3C_T_2us:
11655 val->ui_bus_md = LSM6DSOX_I3C_T_2us;
11656 break;
11657
11658 case LSM6DSOX_I3C_T_1ms:
11659 val->ui_bus_md = LSM6DSOX_I3C_T_1ms;
11660 break;
11661
11662 case LSM6DSOX_I3C_T_25ms:
11663 val->ui_bus_md = LSM6DSOX_I3C_T_25ms;
11664 break;
11665
11666 default:
11667 val->ui_bus_md = LSM6DSOX_SEL_BY_HW;
11668 break;
11669 }
11670 }
11671 }
11672
11673 return ret;
11674}
11675
11687int32_t lsm6dsox_status_get(stmdev_ctx_t *ctx, stmdev_ctx_t *aux_ctx,
11688 lsm6dsox_status_t *val)
11689{
11690 lsm6dsox_spi2_status_reg_ois_t spi2_status_reg_ois;
11691 lsm6dsox_ui_status_reg_ois_t ui_status_reg_ois;
11692 lsm6dsox_status_reg_t status_reg;
11693 lsm6dsox_ctrl3_c_t ctrl3_c;
11694 int32_t ret;
11695 ret = 0;
11696
11697 if (aux_ctx != NULL)
11698 {
11699 ret = lsm6dsox_read_reg(aux_ctx, LSM6DSOX_SPI2_STATUS_REG_OIS,
11700 (uint8_t *)&spi2_status_reg_ois, 1);
11701 val->ois_drdy_xl = spi2_status_reg_ois.xlda;
11702 val->ois_drdy_g = spi2_status_reg_ois.gda;
11703 val->ois_gyro_settling = spi2_status_reg_ois.gyro_settling;
11704 }
11705
11706 if (ctx != NULL)
11707 {
11708 ret = lsm6dsox_read_reg(ctx, LSM6DSOX_CTRL3_C, (uint8_t *)&ctrl3_c, 1);
11709 val->sw_reset = ctrl3_c.sw_reset;
11710 val->boot = ctrl3_c.boot;
11711
11712 if ((ret == 0) && (ctrl3_c.sw_reset == PROPERTY_DISABLE) &&
11713 (ctrl3_c.boot == PROPERTY_DISABLE))
11714 {
11715 ret = lsm6dsox_read_reg(ctx, LSM6DSOX_STATUS_REG,
11716 (uint8_t *)&status_reg, 1);
11717 val->drdy_xl = status_reg.xlda;
11718 val->drdy_g = status_reg.gda;
11719 val->drdy_temp = status_reg.tda;
11720 }
11721
11722 if (aux_ctx == NULL)
11723 {
11724 if (ret == 0)
11725 {
11726 ret = lsm6dsox_read_reg(ctx, LSM6DSOX_UI_STATUS_REG_OIS,
11727 (uint8_t *)&ui_status_reg_ois, 1);
11728 val->ois_drdy_xl = ui_status_reg_ois.xlda;
11729 val->ois_drdy_g = ui_status_reg_ois.gda;
11730 val->ois_gyro_settling = ui_status_reg_ois.gyro_settling;
11731 }
11732 }
11733 }
11734
11735 return ret;
11736}

11747int32_t lsm6dsox_pin_conf_set(stmdev_ctx_t *ctx,
11748 lsm6dsox_pin_conf_t val)
11749{
11750 lsm6dsox_i3c_bus_avb_t i3c_bus_avb;
11751 lsm6dsox_pin_ctrl_t pin_ctrl;
11752 lsm6dsox_ctrl3_c_t ctrl3_c;
11753 int32_t ret;
11754
11755 ret = lsm6dsox_read_reg(ctx, LSM6DSOX_PIN_CTRL, (uint8_t *)&pin_ctrl, 1);
11756
11757 if (ret == 0)
11758 {
11759 pin_ctrl.ois_pu_dis = ~val.aux_sdo_ocs_pull_up;
11760 pin_ctrl.sdo_pu_en = val.sdo_sa0_pull_up;
11761 ret = lsm6dsox_write_reg(ctx, LSM6DSOX_PIN_CTRL, (uint8_t *)&pin_ctrl, 1);
11762 }
11763
11764 if (ret == 0)
11765 {
11766 ret = lsm6dsox_read_reg(ctx, LSM6DSOX_CTRL3_C, (uint8_t *)&ctrl3_c, 1);
11767 }
11768
11769 if (ret == 0)
11770 {
11771 ctrl3_c.pp_od = ~val.int1_int2_push_pull;
11772 ret = lsm6dsox_write_reg(ctx, LSM6DSOX_CTRL3_C, (uint8_t *)&ctrl3_c, 1);
11773 }
11774
11775 if (ret == 0)
11776 {
11777 ret = lsm6dsox_read_reg(ctx, LSM6DSOX_I3C_BUS_AVB,
11778 (uint8_t *)&i3c_bus_avb, 1);
11779 }
11780
11781 if (ret == 0)
11782 {
11783 i3c_bus_avb.pd_dis_int1 = ~val.int1_pull_down;
11784 ret = lsm6dsox_write_reg(ctx, LSM6DSOX_I3C_BUS_AVB,
11785 (uint8_t *)&i3c_bus_avb, 1);
11786 }
11787
11788 return ret;
11789}
11790
11800int32_t lsm6dsox_pin_conf_get(stmdev_ctx_t *ctx,
11801 lsm6dsox_pin_conf_t *val)
11802{
11803 lsm6dsox_i3c_bus_avb_t i3c_bus_avb;
11804 lsm6dsox_pin_ctrl_t pin_ctrl;
11805 lsm6dsox_ctrl3_c_t ctrl3_c;
11806 int32_t ret;
11807
11808 ret = lsm6dsox_read_reg(ctx, LSM6DSOX_PIN_CTRL, (uint8_t *)&pin_ctrl, 1);
11809
11810 if (ret == 0)
11811 {
11812 val->aux_sdo_ocs_pull_up = ~pin_ctrl.ois_pu_dis;
11813 val->aux_sdo_ocs_pull_up = pin_ctrl.sdo_pu_en;
11814 ret = lsm6dsox_read_reg(ctx, LSM6DSOX_CTRL3_C, (uint8_t *)&ctrl3_c, 1);
11815 }
11816
11817 if (ret == 0)
11818 {
11819 val->int1_int2_push_pull = ~ctrl3_c.pp_od;
11820 ret = lsm6dsox_read_reg(ctx, LSM6DSOX_I3C_BUS_AVB,
11821 (uint8_t *)&i3c_bus_avb, 1);
11822 }
11823
11824 if (ret == 0)
11825 {
11826 val->int1_pull_down = ~i3c_bus_avb.pd_dis_int1;
11827 }
11828
11829 return ret;
11830}

11840int32_t lsm6dsox_interrupt_mode_set(stmdev_ctx_t *ctx,
11841 lsm6dsox_int_mode_t val)
11842{
11843 lsm6dsox_tap_cfg0_t tap_cfg0;
11844 lsm6dsox_page_rw_t page_rw;
11845 lsm6dsox_ctrl3_c_t ctrl3_c;
11846 int32_t ret;
11847
11848 ret = lsm6dsox_read_reg(ctx, LSM6DSOX_CTRL3_C, (uint8_t *)&ctrl3_c, 1);
11849
11850 if (ret == 0)
11851 {
11852 ctrl3_c.h_lactive = val.active_low;
11853 ret = lsm6dsox_write_reg(ctx, LSM6DSOX_CTRL3_C, (uint8_t *)&ctrl3_c, 1);
11854 }
11855
11856 if (ret == 0)
11857 {
11858 ret = lsm6dsox_read_reg(ctx, LSM6DSOX_TAP_CFG0, (uint8_t *) &tap_cfg0, 1);
11859 }
11860
11861 if (ret == 0)
11862 {
11863 tap_cfg0.lir = val.base_latched;
11864 tap_cfg0.int_clr_on_read = val.base_latched | val.emb_latched;
11865 ret = lsm6dsox_write_reg(ctx, LSM6DSOX_TAP_CFG0,
11866 (uint8_t *) &tap_cfg0, 1);
11867 }
11868
11869 if (ret == 0)
11870 {
11871 ret = lsm6dsox_mem_bank_set(ctx, LSM6DSOX_EMBEDDED_FUNC_BANK);
11872 }
11873
11874 if (ret == 0)
11875 {
11876 ret = lsm6dsox_read_reg(ctx, LSM6DSOX_PAGE_RW, (uint8_t *) &page_rw, 1);
11877 }
11878
11879 if (ret == 0)
11880 {
11881 page_rw.emb_func_lir = val.emb_latched;
11882 ret = lsm6dsox_write_reg(ctx, LSM6DSOX_PAGE_RW, (uint8_t *) &page_rw, 1);
11883 }
11884
11885 if (ret == 0)
11886 {
11887 ret = lsm6dsox_mem_bank_set(ctx, LSM6DSOX_USER_BANK);
11888 }
11889
11890 return ret;
11891}

11933 }

11938 }

12013 if (ret == 0)
12014 {

12016 {
12017 ctrl4_c.int2_on_int1 = PROPERTY_ENABLE;
12018 }

12020 else

12022 ctrl4_c.int2_on_int1 = PROPERTY_DISABLE;

12026 }

12031 }

12036 (uint8_t *)&mlc_int1, 1);

12040 {
12041 ret = lsm6dsox_write_reg(ctx, LSM6DSOX_EMB_FUNC_INT1,
12042 (uint8_t *)&emb_func_int1, 1);
12043 }
12044
12045 if (ret == 0)
12046 {
12047 ret = lsm6dsox_write_reg(ctx, LSM6DSOX_FSM_INT1_A,
12048 (uint8_t *)&fsm_int1_a, 1);
12049 }
12050
