12602 if (ctx != NULL)
12603 {
12604 if (ret == 0)
12605 {
12606 ret = lsm6dsox_mem_bank_set(ctx, LSM6DSOX_EMBEDDED_FUNC_BANK);
12607 }
12608
12609 if (ret == 0)
12610 {
12611 ret = lsm6dsox_read_reg(ctx, LSM6DSOX_MLC_INT2,
12612 (uint8_t *)&mlc_int2, 1);
12613 }
12614
12615 if (ret == 0)
12616 {
12617 ret = lsm6dsox_read_reg(ctx, LSM6DSOX_EMB_FUNC_INT2,
12618 (uint8_t *)&emb_func_int2, 1);
12619 }
12620
12621 if (ret == 0)
12622 {
12623 ret = lsm6dsox_read_reg(ctx, LSM6DSOX_FSM_INT2_A,
12624 (uint8_t *)&fsm_int2_a, 1);
12625 }
12626
12627 if (ret == 0)
12628 {
12629 ret = lsm6dsox_read_reg(ctx, LSM6DSOX_FSM_INT2_B,
12630 (uint8_t *)&fsm_int2_b, 1);
12631 }
12632
12633 if (ret == 0)
12634 {
12635 ret = lsm6dsox_mem_bank_set(ctx, LSM6DSOX_USER_BANK);
12636 }
12637
12638 if (ret == 0)
12639 {
12640 ret = lsm6dsox_read_reg(ctx, LSM6DSOX_INT2_CTRL,
12641 (uint8_t *)&int2_ctrl, 1);
12642 }
12643
12644 if (ret == 0)
12645 {
12646 ret = lsm6dsox_read_reg(ctx, LSM6DSOX_MD2_CFG,
12647 (uint8_t *)&md2_cfg, 1);
12648 }
12649
12650 if (ret == 0)
12651 {
12652 ret = lsm6dsox_read_reg(ctx, LSM6DSOX_CTRL4_C, (uint8_t *)&ctrl4_c, 1);
12653 }
12654
12655 if (ctrl4_c.int2_on_int1 == PROPERTY_DISABLE)
12656 {
12657 if (ret == 0)
12658 {
12659 ret = lsm6dsox_read_reg(ctx, LSM6DSOX_INT2_CTRL,
12660 (uint8_t *)&int2_ctrl, 1);
12661 val->drdy_temp = int2_ctrl.int2_drdy_temp;
12662 }
12663
12664 if (ret == 0)
12665 {
12666 ret = lsm6dsox_read_reg(ctx, LSM6DSOX_MD2_CFG, (uint8_t *)&md2_cfg, 1);
12667 val->timestamp = md2_cfg.int2_timestamp;
12668 }
12669 }
12670
12671 else
12672 {
12673 val->drdy_temp = PROPERTY_DISABLE;
12674 val->timestamp = PROPERTY_DISABLE;
12675 }
12676
12677 val->drdy_xl = int2_ctrl.int2_drdy_xl;
12678 val->drdy_g = int2_ctrl.int2_drdy_g;
12679 val->drdy_temp = int2_ctrl.int2_drdy_temp;
12680 val->fifo_th = int2_ctrl.int2_fifo_th;
12681 val->fifo_ovr = int2_ctrl.int2_fifo_ovr;
12682 val->fifo_full = int2_ctrl.int2_fifo_full;
12683 val->fifo_bdr = int2_ctrl.int2_cnt_bdr;
12684 val->timestamp = md2_cfg.int2_timestamp;
12685 val->six_d = md2_cfg.int2_6d;
12686 val->double_tap = md2_cfg.int2_double_tap;
12687 val->free_fall = md2_cfg.int2_ff;
12688 val->wake_up = md2_cfg.int2_wu;
12689 val->single_tap = md2_cfg.int2_single_tap;
12690 val->sleep_change = md2_cfg.int2_sleep_change;
12691 val->step_detector = emb_func_int2. int2_step_detector;
12692 val->tilt = emb_func_int2.int2_tilt;
12693 val->fsm_lc = emb_func_int2.int2_fsm_lc;
12694 val->fsm1 = fsm_int2_a.int2_fsm1;
12695 val->fsm2 = fsm_int2_a.int2_fsm2;
12696 val->fsm3 = fsm_int2_a.int2_fsm3;
12697 val->fsm4 = fsm_int2_a.int2_fsm4;
12698 val->fsm5 = fsm_int2_a.int2_fsm5;
12699 val->fsm6 = fsm_int2_a.int2_fsm6;
12700 val->fsm7 = fsm_int2_a.int2_fsm7;
12701 val->fsm8 = fsm_int2_a.int2_fsm8;
12702 val->fsm9 = fsm_int2_b.int2_fsm9;
12703 val->fsm10 = fsm_int2_b.int2_fsm10;
12704 val->fsm11 = fsm_int2_b.int2_fsm11;
12705 val->fsm12 = fsm_int2_b.int2_fsm12;
12706 val->fsm13 = fsm_int2_b.int2_fsm13;
12707 val->fsm14 = fsm_int2_b.int2_fsm14;
12708 val->fsm15 = fsm_int2_b.int2_fsm15;
12709 val->fsm16 = fsm_int2_b.int2_fsm16;
12710 val->mlc1 = mlc_int2.int2_mlc1;
12711 val->mlc2 = mlc_int2.int2_mlc2;
12712 val->mlc3 = mlc_int2.int2_mlc3;
12713 val->mlc4 = mlc_int2.int2_mlc4;
12714 val->mlc5 = mlc_int2.int2_mlc5;
12715 val->mlc6 = mlc_int2.int2_mlc6;
12716 val->mlc7 = mlc_int2.int2_mlc7;
12717 val->mlc8 = mlc_int2.int2_mlc8;
12718 }
12719
12720 return ret;
12721}
12722
12731int32_t lsm6dsox_all_sources_get(stmdev_ctx_t *ctx,
12732 lsm6dsox_all_sources_t *val)
12733{
12734 lsm6dsox_emb_func_status_mainpage_t emb_func_status_mainpage;
12735 lsm6dsox_status_master_mainpage_t status_master_mainpage;
12736 lsm6dsox_fsm_status_a_mainpage_t fsm_status_a_mainpage;
12737 lsm6dsox_fsm_status_b_mainpage_t fsm_status_b_mainpage;
12738 lsm6dsox_mlc_status_mainpage_t mlc_status_mainpage;
12739 lsm6dsox_fifo_status1_t fifo_status1;
12740 lsm6dsox_fifo_status2_t fifo_status2;
12741 lsm6dsox_all_int_src_t all_int_src;
12742 lsm6dsox_wake_up_src_t wake_up_src;
12743 lsm6dsox_status_reg_t status_reg;
12744 lsm6dsox_tap_src_t tap_src;
12745 lsm6dsox_d6d_src_t d6d_src;
12746 lsm6dsox_ctrl5_c_t ctrl5_c;
12747 uint8_t reg[12];
12748 int32_t ret;
12749 ret = lsm6dsox_read_reg(ctx, LSM6DSOX_CTRL5_C, (uint8_t *)&ctrl5_c, 1);
12750
12751 if (ret == 0)
12752 {
12753 ctrl5_c.rounding_status = PROPERTY_ENABLE;
12754 ret = lsm6dsox_write_reg(ctx, LSM6DSOX_CTRL5_C, (uint8_t *)&ctrl5_c, 1);
12755 }
12756
12757 if (ret == 0)
12758 {
12759 ret = lsm6dsox_read_reg(ctx, LSM6DSOX_ALL_INT_SRC, reg, 12);
12760 }
12761
12762 if (ret == 0)
12763 {
12764 bytecpy((uint8_t *)&all_int_src, &reg[0]);
12765 bytecpy((uint8_t *)&wake_up_src, &reg[1]);
12766 bytecpy((uint8_t *)&tap_src, &reg[2]);
12767 bytecpy((uint8_t *)&d6d_src, &reg[3]);
12768 bytecpy((uint8_t *)&status_reg, &reg[4]);
12769 bytecpy((uint8_t *)&emb_func_status_mainpage, &reg[5]);
12770 bytecpy((uint8_t *)&fsm_status_a_mainpage, &reg[6]);
12771 bytecpy((uint8_t *)&fsm_status_b_mainpage, &reg[7]);
12772 bytecpy((uint8_t *)&mlc_status_mainpage, &reg[8]);
12773 bytecpy((uint8_t *)&status_master_mainpage, &reg[9]);
12774 bytecpy((uint8_t *)&fifo_status1, &reg[10]);
12775 bytecpy((uint8_t *)&fifo_status2, &reg[11]);
12776 val->timestamp = all_int_src.timestamp_endcount;
12777 val->wake_up_z = wake_up_src.z_wu;
12778 val->wake_up_y = wake_up_src.y_wu;
12779 val->wake_up_x = wake_up_src.x_wu;
12780 val->wake_up = wake_up_src.wu_ia;
12781 val->sleep_state = wake_up_src.sleep_state;
12782 val->free_fall = wake_up_src.ff_ia;
12783 val->sleep_change = wake_up_src.sleep_change_ia;
12784 val->tap_x = tap_src.x_tap;
12785 val->tap_y = tap_src.y_tap;
12786 val->tap_z = tap_src.z_tap;
12787 val->tap_sign = tap_src.tap_sign;
12788 val->double_tap = tap_src.double_tap;
12789 val->single_tap = tap_src.single_tap;
12790 val->six_d_xl = d6d_src.xl;
12791 val->six_d_xh = d6d_src.xh;
12792 val->six_d_yl = d6d_src.yl;
12793 val->six_d_yh = d6d_src.yh;
12794 val->six_d_zl = d6d_src.zl;
12795 val->six_d_zh = d6d_src.zh;
12796 val->six_d = d6d_src.d6d_ia;
12797 val->den_flag = d6d_src.den_drdy;
12798 val->drdy_xl = status_reg.xlda;
12799 val->drdy_g = status_reg.gda;
12800 val->drdy_temp = status_reg.tda;
12801 val->step_detector = emb_func_status_mainpage.is_step_det;
12802 val->tilt = emb_func_status_mainpage.is_tilt;
12803 val->sig_mot = emb_func_status_mainpage.is_sigmot;
12804 val->fsm_lc = emb_func_status_mainpage.is_fsm_lc;
12805 val->fsm1 = fsm_status_a_mainpage.is_fsm1;
12806 val->fsm2 = fsm_status_a_mainpage.is_fsm2;
12807 val->fsm3 = fsm_status_a_mainpage.is_fsm3;
12808 val->fsm4 = fsm_status_a_mainpage.is_fsm4;
12809 val->fsm5 = fsm_status_a_mainpage.is_fsm5;
12810 val->fsm6 = fsm_status_a_mainpage.is_fsm6;
12811 val->fsm7 = fsm_status_a_mainpage.is_fsm7;
12812 val->fsm8 = fsm_status_a_mainpage.is_fsm8;
12813 val->fsm9 = fsm_status_b_mainpage.is_fsm9;
12814 val->fsm10 = fsm_status_b_mainpage.is_fsm10;
12815 val->fsm11 = fsm_status_b_mainpage.is_fsm11;
12816 val->fsm12 = fsm_status_b_mainpage.is_fsm12;
12817 val->fsm13 = fsm_status_b_mainpage.is_fsm13;
12818 val->fsm14 = fsm_status_b_mainpage.is_fsm14;
12819 val->fsm15 = fsm_status_b_mainpage.is_fsm15;
12820 val->fsm16 = fsm_status_b_mainpage.is_fsm16;
12821 val->mlc1 = mlc_status_mainpage.is_mlc1;
12822 val->mlc2 = mlc_status_mainpage.is_mlc2;
12823 val->mlc3 = mlc_status_mainpage.is_mlc3;
12824 val->mlc4 = mlc_status_mainpage.is_mlc4;
12825 val->mlc5 = mlc_status_mainpage.is_mlc5;
12826 val->mlc6 = mlc_status_mainpage.is_mlc6;
12827 val->mlc7 = mlc_status_mainpage.is_mlc7;
12828 val->mlc8 = mlc_status_mainpage.is_mlc8;
12829 val->sh_endop = status_master_mainpage.sens_hub_endop;
12830 val->sh_slave0_nack = status_master_mainpage.slave0_nack;
12831 val->sh_slave1_nack = status_master_mainpage.slave1_nack;
12832 val->sh_slave2_nack = status_master_mainpage.slave2_nack;
12833 val->sh_slave3_nack = status_master_mainpage.slave3_nack;
12834 val->sh_wr_once = status_master_mainpage.wr_once_done;
12835 val->fifo_diff = (256U * fifo_status2.diff_fifo) +
12836 fifo_status1.diff_fifo;
12837 val->fifo_ovr_latched = fifo_status2.over_run_latched;
12838 val->fifo_bdr = fifo_status2.counter_bdr_ia;
12839 val->fifo_full = fifo_status2.fifo_full_ia;
12840 val->fifo_ovr = fifo_status2.fifo_ovr_ia;
12841 val->fifo_th = fifo_status2.fifo_wtm_ia;
12842 ctrl5_c.rounding_status = PROPERTY_DISABLE;
12843 ret = lsm6dsox_write_reg(ctx, LSM6DSOX_CTRL5_C, (uint8_t *)&ctrl5_c, 1);
12844 }
12845
12846 return ret;
12847}
12848
12861int32_t lsm6dsox_mode_set(stmdev_ctx_t *ctx, stmdev_ctx_t *aux_ctx,
12862 lsm6dsox_md_t *val)
12863{
12864 lsm6dsox_func_cfg_access_t func_cfg_access;
12865 lsm6dsox_spi2_ctrl1_ois_t spi2_ctrl1_ois;
12866 lsm6dsox_spi2_ctrl2_ois_t spi2_ctrl2_ois;
12867 lsm6dsox_spi2_ctrl3_ois_t spi2_ctrl3_ois;
12868 lsm6dsox_ui_ctrl1_ois_t ui_ctrl1_ois;
12869 lsm6dsox_ui_ctrl2_ois_t ui_ctrl2_ois;
12870 lsm6dsox_ui_ctrl3_ois_t ui_ctrl3_ois;
12871 lsm6dsox_ctrl1_xl_t ctrl1_xl;
12872 lsm6dsox_ctrl8_xl_t ctrl8_xl;
12873 lsm6dsox_ctrl2_g_t ctrl2_g;
12874 lsm6dsox_ctrl3_c_t ctrl3_c;
12875 lsm6dsox_ctrl4_c_t ctrl4_c;
12876 lsm6dsox_ctrl5_c_t ctrl5_c;
12877 lsm6dsox_ctrl6_c_t ctrl6_c;
12878 lsm6dsox_ctrl7_g_t ctrl7_g;
12879 uint8_t xl_hm_mode;
12880 uint8_t g_hm_mode;
12881 uint8_t xl_ulp_en;
12882 uint8_t odr_gy;
12883 uint8_t odr_xl;
12884 uint8_t reg[8];
12885 int32_t ret;
12886
12887 ret = 0;
12888 /* FIXME: Remove warnings with STM32CubeIDE */
12889 ctrl3_c.not_used_01 = 0;
12890 ctrl4_c.not_used_01 = 0;
12891 ctrl5_c.xl_ulp_en = 0;
12892 /* reading input configuration */
12893 xl_hm_mode = ((uint8_t)val->ui.xl.odr & 0x10U) >> 4;
12894 xl_ulp_en = ((uint8_t)val->ui.xl.odr & 0x20U) >> 5;
12895 odr_xl = (uint8_t)val->ui.xl.odr & 0x0FU;
12896
12897 /* if enable xl ultra low power mode disable gy and OIS chain */
12898 if (xl_ulp_en == PROPERTY_ENABLE)
12899 {
12900 val->ois.xl.odr = LSM6DSOX_XL_OIS_OFF;
12901 val->ois.gy.odr = LSM6DSOX_GY_OIS_OFF;
12902 val->ui.gy.odr = LSM6DSOX_GY_UI_OFF;
12903 }
12904
12905 /* if OIS xl is enabled also gyro OIS is enabled */
12906 if (val->ois.xl.odr == LSM6DSOX_XL_OIS_6667Hz_HP)
12907 {
12908 val->ois.gy.odr = LSM6DSOX_GY_OIS_6667Hz_HP;
12909 }
12910
12911 g_hm_mode = ((uint8_t)val->ui.gy.odr & 0x10U) >> 4;
12912 odr_gy = (uint8_t)val->ui.gy.odr & 0x0FU;
12913
12914 /* reading registers to be configured */
12915 if (ctx != NULL)
12916 {
12917 ret = lsm6dsox_read_reg(ctx, LSM6DSOX_CTRL1_XL, reg, 8);
12918 bytecpy((uint8_t *)&ctrl1_xl, &reg[0]);
12919 bytecpy((uint8_t *)&ctrl2_g, &reg[1]);
12920 bytecpy((uint8_t *)&ctrl3_c, &reg[2]);
12921 bytecpy((uint8_t *)&ctrl4_c, &reg[3]);
12922 bytecpy((uint8_t *)&ctrl5_c, &reg[4]);
12923 bytecpy((uint8_t *)&ctrl6_c, &reg[5]);
12924 bytecpy((uint8_t *)&ctrl7_g, &reg[6]);
12925 bytecpy((uint8_t *)&ctrl8_xl, &reg[7]);
12926
12927 if (ret == 0)
12928 {
12929 ret = lsm6dsox_read_reg(ctx, LSM6DSOX_FUNC_CFG_ACCESS,
12930 (uint8_t *)&func_cfg_access, 1);
12931 }
12932
12933 /* if toggle xl ultra low power mode, turn off xl before reconfigure */
12934 if (ctrl5_c.xl_ulp_en != xl_ulp_en)
12935 {
12936 ctrl1_xl.odr_xl = (uint8_t) 0x00U;
12937 ret = lsm6dsox_write_reg(ctx, LSM6DSOX_CTRL1_XL,
12938 (uint8_t *)&ctrl1_xl, 1);
12939 }
12940 }
12941
12942 /* reading OIS registers to be configured */
12943 if (aux_ctx != NULL)
12944 {
12945 if (ret == 0)
12946 {
12947 ret = lsm6dsox_read_reg(aux_ctx, LSM6DSOX_SPI2_CTRL1_OIS, reg, 3);
12948 }
12949
12950 bytecpy((uint8_t *)&spi2_ctrl1_ois, &reg[0]);
12951 bytecpy((uint8_t *)&spi2_ctrl2_ois, &reg[1]);
12952 bytecpy((uint8_t *)&spi2_ctrl3_ois, &reg[2]);
12953 }
12954
12955 else
12956 {
12957 if (ctx != NULL)
12958 {
12959 if (ret == 0)
12960 {
12961 ret = lsm6dsox_read_reg(ctx, LSM6DSOX_UI_CTRL1_OIS, reg, 3);
12962 }
12963
12964 bytecpy((uint8_t *)&ui_ctrl1_ois, &reg[0]);
12965 bytecpy((uint8_t *)&ui_ctrl2_ois, &reg[1]);
12966 bytecpy((uint8_t *)&ui_ctrl3_ois, &reg[2]);
12967 }
12968 }
12969
12970 /* Check the Finite State Machine data rate constraints */
12971 if (val->fsm.sens != LSM6DSOX_FSM_DISABLE)
12972 {
12973 switch (val->fsm.odr)
12974 {
12975 case LSM6DSOX_FSM_12Hz5:
12976 if ((val->fsm.sens != LSM6DSOX_FSM_GY) && (odr_xl == 0x00U))
12977 {
12978 odr_xl = 0x01U;
12979 }
12980
12981 if ((val->fsm.sens != LSM6DSOX_FSM_XL) && (odr_gy == 0x00U))
12982 {
12983 xl_ulp_en = PROPERTY_DISABLE;
12984 odr_gy = 0x01U;
12985 }
12986
12987 break;
12988
12989 case LSM6DSOX_FSM_26Hz:
12990 if ((val->fsm.sens != LSM6DSOX_FSM_GY) && (odr_xl < 0x02U))
12991 {
12992 odr_xl = 0x02U;
12993 }
12994
12995 if ((val->fsm.sens != LSM6DSOX_FSM_XL) && (odr_gy < 0x02U))
12996 {
12997 xl_ulp_en = PROPERTY_DISABLE;
12998 odr_gy = 0x02U;
12999 }
13000
13001 break;
13002
13003 case LSM6DSOX_FSM_52Hz:
13004 if ((val->fsm.sens != LSM6DSOX_FSM_GY) && (odr_xl < 0x03U))
13005 {
13006 odr_xl = 0x03U;
13007 }
13008
13009 if ((val->fsm.sens != LSM6DSOX_FSM_XL) && (odr_gy < 0x03U))
13010 {
13011 xl_ulp_en = PROPERTY_DISABLE;
13012 odr_gy = 0x03U;
13013 }
13014
13015 break;
13016
13017 case LSM6DSOX_FSM_104Hz:
13018 if ((val->fsm.sens != LSM6DSOX_FSM_GY) && (odr_xl < 0x04U))
13019 {
13020 odr_xl = 0x04U;
13021 }
13022
13023 if ((val->fsm.sens != LSM6DSOX_FSM_XL) && (odr_gy < 0x04U))
13024 {
13025 xl_ulp_en = PROPERTY_DISABLE;
13026 odr_gy = 0x04U;
13027 }
13028
13029 break;
13030
13031 default:
13032 odr_xl = 0x00U;
13033 odr_gy = 0x00U;
13034 break;
13035 }
13036 }
13037
13038 /* Check the Machine Learning Core data rate constraints */
13039 if (val->mlc.sens != LSM6DSOX_MLC_DISABLE)
13040 {
13041 switch (val->mlc.odr)
13042 {
13043 case LSM6DSOX_MLC_12Hz5:
13044 if (odr_xl == 0x00U)
13045 {
13046 odr_xl = 0x01U;
13047 }
13048
13049 if ((val->mlc.sens != LSM6DSOX_MLC_XL) && (odr_gy == 0x00U))
13050 {
13051 xl_ulp_en = PROPERTY_DISABLE;
13052 odr_gy = 0x01U;
13053 }
13054
13055 break;
13056
13057 case LSM6DSOX_MLC_26Hz:
13058 if (odr_xl < 0x02U)
13059 {
13060 odr_xl = 0x02U;
13061 }
13062
13063 if ((val->mlc.sens != LSM6DSOX_MLC_XL) && (odr_gy < 0x02U))
13064 {
13065 xl_ulp_en = PROPERTY_DISABLE;
13066 odr_gy = 0x02U;
13067 }
13068
13069 break;
13070
13071 case LSM6DSOX_MLC_52Hz:
13072 if (odr_xl < 0x03U)
13073 {
13074 odr_xl = 0x03U;
13075 }
13076
13077 if ((val->mlc.sens != LSM6DSOX_MLC_XL) && (odr_gy < 0x03U))
13078 {
13079 xl_ulp_en = PROPERTY_DISABLE;
13080 odr_gy = 0x03U;
13081 }
13082
13083 break;
13084
13085 case LSM6DSOX_MLC_104Hz:
13086 if (odr_xl < 0x04U)
13087 {
13088 odr_xl = 0x04U;
13089 }
13090
13091 if ((val->mlc.sens != LSM6DSOX_MLC_XL) && (odr_gy < 0x04U))
13092 {
13093 xl_ulp_en = PROPERTY_DISABLE;
13094 odr_gy = 0x04U;
13095 }
13096
13097 break;
13098
13099 default:
13100 odr_xl = 0x00U;
13101 odr_gy = 0x00U;
13102 break;
13103 }
13104 }
13105
13106 /* Updating the accelerometer data rate configuration */
13107 switch ((ctrl5_c.xl_ulp_en << 5) | (ctrl6_c.xl_hm_mode << 4) |
13108 ctrl1_xl.odr_xl)
13109 {
13110 case LSM6DSOX_XL_UI_OFF:
13111 val->ui.xl.odr = LSM6DSOX_XL_UI_OFF;
13112 break;
13113
13114 case LSM6DSOX_XL_UI_12Hz5_HP:
13115 val->ui.xl.odr = LSM6DSOX_XL_UI_12Hz5_HP;
13116 break;
13117
13118 case LSM6DSOX_XL_UI_26Hz_HP:
13119 val->ui.xl.odr = LSM6DSOX_XL_UI_26Hz_HP;
13120 break;
13121
13122 case LSM6DSOX_XL_UI_52Hz_HP:
13123 val->ui.xl.odr = LSM6DSOX_XL_UI_52Hz_HP;
13124 break;
13125
13126 case LSM6DSOX_XL_UI_104Hz_HP:
13127 val->ui.xl.odr = LSM6DSOX_XL_UI_104Hz_HP;
13128 break;
13129
13130 case LSM6DSOX_XL_UI_208Hz_HP:
13131 val->ui.xl.odr = LSM6DSOX_XL_UI_208Hz_HP;
13132 break;
13133
13134 case LSM6DSOX_XL_UI_416Hz_HP:
13135 val->ui.xl.odr = LSM6DSOX_XL_UI_416Hz_HP;
13136 break;
13137
13138 case LSM6DSOX_XL_UI_833Hz_HP:
13139 val->ui.xl.odr = LSM6DSOX_XL_UI_833Hz_HP;
13140 break;
13141
13142 case LSM6DSOX_XL_UI_1667Hz_HP:
13143 val->ui.xl.odr = LSM6DSOX_XL_UI_1667Hz_HP;
13144 break;
13145
13146 case LSM6DSOX_XL_UI_3333Hz_HP:
13147 val->ui.xl.odr = LSM6DSOX_XL_UI_3333Hz_HP;
13148 break;
13149
13150 case LSM6DSOX_XL_UI_6667Hz_HP:
13151 val->ui.xl.odr = LSM6DSOX_XL_UI_6667Hz_HP;
13152 break;
13153
13154 case LSM6DSOX_XL_UI_1Hz6_LP:
13155 val->ui.xl.odr = LSM6DSOX_XL_UI_1Hz6_LP;
13156 break;
13157
13158 case LSM6DSOX_XL_UI_12Hz5_LP:
13159 val->ui.xl.odr = LSM6DSOX_XL_UI_12Hz5_LP;
13160 break;
13161
13162 case LSM6DSOX_XL_UI_26Hz_LP:
13163 val->ui.xl.odr = LSM6DSOX_XL_UI_26Hz_LP;
13164 break;
13165
13166 case LSM6DSOX_XL_UI_52Hz_LP:
13167 val->ui.xl.odr = LSM6DSOX_XL_UI_52Hz_LP;
13168 break;
13169
13170 case LSM6DSOX_XL_UI_104Hz_NM:
13171 val->ui.xl.odr = LSM6DSOX_XL_UI_104Hz_NM;
13172 break;
13173
13174 case LSM6DSOX_XL_UI_208Hz_NM:
13175 val->ui.xl.odr = LSM6DSOX_XL_UI_208Hz_NM;
13176 break;
13177
13178 case LSM6DSOX_XL_UI_1Hz6_ULP:
13179 val->ui.xl.odr = LSM6DSOX_XL_UI_1Hz6_ULP;
13180 break;
13181
13182 case LSM6DSOX_XL_UI_12Hz5_ULP:
13183 val->ui.xl.odr = LSM6DSOX_XL_UI_12Hz5_ULP;
13184 break;
13185
13186 case LSM6DSOX_XL_UI_26Hz_ULP:
13187 val->ui.xl.odr = LSM6DSOX_XL_UI_26Hz_ULP;
13188 break;
13189
13190 case LSM6DSOX_XL_UI_52Hz_ULP:
13191 val->ui.xl.odr = LSM6DSOX_XL_UI_52Hz_ULP;
13192 break;
13193
13194 case LSM6DSOX_XL_UI_104Hz_ULP:
13195 val->ui.xl.odr = LSM6DSOX_XL_UI_104Hz_ULP;
13196 break;
13197
13198 case LSM6DSOX_XL_UI_208Hz_ULP:
13199 val->ui.xl.odr = LSM6DSOX_XL_UI_208Hz_ULP;
13200 break;
13201
13202 default:
13203 val->ui.xl.odr = LSM6DSOX_XL_UI_OFF;
13204 break;
13205 }
13206
13207 /* Updating the accelerometer data rate configuration */
13208 switch ((ctrl7_g.g_hm_mode << 4) | ctrl2_g.odr_g)
13209 {
13210 case LSM6DSOX_GY_UI_OFF:
13211 val->ui.gy.odr = LSM6DSOX_GY_UI_OFF;
13212 break;
13213
13214 case LSM6DSOX_GY_UI_12Hz5_LP:
13215 val->ui.gy.odr = LSM6DSOX_GY_UI_12Hz5_LP;
13216 break;
13217
13218 case LSM6DSOX_GY_UI_12Hz5_HP:
13219 val->ui.gy.odr = LSM6DSOX_GY_UI_12Hz5_HP;
13220 break;
13221
13222 case LSM6DSOX_GY_UI_26Hz_LP:
13223 val->ui.gy.odr = LSM6DSOX_GY_UI_26Hz_LP;
13224 break;
13225
13226 case LSM6DSOX_GY_UI_26Hz_HP:
13227 val->ui.gy.odr = LSM6DSOX_GY_UI_26Hz_HP;
13228 break;
13229
13230 case LSM6DSOX_GY_UI_52Hz_LP:
13231 val->ui.gy.odr = LSM6DSOX_GY_UI_52Hz_LP;
13232 break;
13233
13234 case LSM6DSOX_GY_UI_52Hz_HP:
13235 val->ui.gy.odr = LSM6DSOX_GY_UI_52Hz_HP;
13236 break;
13237
13238 case LSM6DSOX_GY_UI_104Hz_NM:
13239 val->ui.gy.odr = LSM6DSOX_GY_UI_104Hz_NM;
13240 break;
13241
13242 case LSM6DSOX_GY_UI_104Hz_HP:
13243 val->ui.gy.odr = LSM6DSOX_GY_UI_104Hz_HP;
13244 break;
13245
13246 case LSM6DSOX_GY_UI_208Hz_NM:
13247 val->ui.gy.odr = LSM6DSOX_GY_UI_208Hz_NM;
13248 break;
13249
13250 case LSM6DSOX_GY_UI_208Hz_HP:
13251 val->ui.gy.odr = LSM6DSOX_GY_UI_208Hz_HP;
13252 break;
13253
13254 case LSM6DSOX_GY_UI_416Hz_HP:
13255 val->ui.gy.odr = LSM6DSOX_GY_UI_416Hz_HP;
13256 break;
13257
13258 case LSM6DSOX_GY_UI_833Hz_HP:
13259 val->ui.gy.odr = LSM6DSOX_GY_UI_833Hz_HP;
13260 break;
13261
13262 case LSM6DSOX_GY_UI_1667Hz_HP:
13263 val->ui.gy.odr = LSM6DSOX_GY_UI_1667Hz_HP;
13264 break;
13265
13266 case LSM6DSOX_GY_UI_3333Hz_HP:
13267 val->ui.gy.odr = LSM6DSOX_GY_UI_3333Hz_HP;
13268 break;
13269
13270 case LSM6DSOX_GY_UI_6667Hz_HP:
13271 val->ui.gy.odr = LSM6DSOX_GY_UI_6667Hz_HP;
13272 break;
13273
13274 default:
13275 val->ui.gy.odr = LSM6DSOX_GY_UI_OFF;
13276 break;
13277 }
13278
13279 /* Check accelerometer full scale constraints */
13280 /* Full scale of 16g must be the same for UI and OIS */
13281 if ((val->ui.xl.fs == LSM6DSOX_XL_UI_16g) ||
13282 (val->ois.xl.fs == LSM6DSOX_XL_OIS_16g))
13283 {
13284 val->ui.xl.fs = LSM6DSOX_XL_UI_16g;
13285 val->ois.xl.fs = LSM6DSOX_XL_OIS_16g;
13286 }
13287
13288 /* prapare new configuration */
13289
13290 /* Full scale of 16g must be the same for UI and OIS */
13291 if (val->ui.xl.fs == LSM6DSOX_XL_UI_16g)
13292 {
13293 ctrl8_xl.xl_fs_mode = PROPERTY_DISABLE;
13294 }
13295
13296 else
13297 {
13298 ctrl8_xl.xl_fs_mode = PROPERTY_ENABLE;
13299 }
13300
13301 /* OIS new configuration */
13302 ctrl7_g.ois_on_en = val->ois.ctrl_md & 0x01U;
13303 func_cfg_access.ois_ctrl_from_ui = (val->ois.ctrl_md & 0x02U) >> 1;
13304
13305 switch (val->ois.ctrl_md)
13306 {
13307 case LSM6DSOX_OIS_ONLY_AUX:
13308 spi2_ctrl1_ois.fs_g_ois = (uint8_t)val->ois.gy.fs;
13309 spi2_ctrl1_ois.ois_en_spi2 = (uint8_t)val->ois.gy.odr |
13310 (uint8_t)val->ois.xl.odr;
13311 spi2_ctrl1_ois.mode4_en = (uint8_t) val->ois.xl.odr;
13312 spi2_ctrl3_ois.fs_xl_ois = (uint8_t)val->ois.xl.fs;
13313 break;
13314
13315 case LSM6DSOX_OIS_ONLY_UI:
13316 ui_ctrl1_ois.fs_g_ois = (uint8_t)val->ois.gy.fs;
13317 ui_ctrl1_ois.ois_en_spi2 = (uint8_t)val->ois.gy.odr |
13318 (uint8_t)val->ois.xl.odr;
13319 ui_ctrl1_ois.mode4_en = (uint8_t)val->ois.xl.odr;
13320 ui_ctrl3_ois.fs_xl_ois = (uint8_t)val->ois.xl.fs;
13321 break;
13322
13323 case LSM6DSOX_OIS_MIXED:
13324 spi2_ctrl1_ois.fs_g_ois = (uint8_t)val->ois.gy.fs;
13325 ctrl7_g.ois_on = (uint8_t)val->ois.gy.odr | (uint8_t)val->ois.xl.odr;
13326 spi2_ctrl1_ois.mode4_en = (uint8_t) val->ois.xl.odr;
13327 spi2_ctrl3_ois.fs_xl_ois = (uint8_t)val->ois.xl.fs;
13328 break;
13329
13330 default:
13331 spi2_ctrl1_ois.fs_g_ois = (uint8_t)val->ois.gy.fs;
13332 spi2_ctrl1_ois.ois_en_spi2 = (uint8_t)val->ois.gy.odr |
13333 (uint8_t)val->ois.xl.odr;
13334 spi2_ctrl1_ois.mode4_en = (uint8_t) val->ois.xl.odr;
13335 spi2_ctrl3_ois.fs_xl_ois = (uint8_t)val->ois.xl.fs;
13336 break;
13337 }
13338
13339 /* UI new configuration */
13340 ctrl1_xl.odr_xl = odr_xl;
13341 ctrl1_xl.fs_xl = (uint8_t)val->ui.xl.fs;
13342 ctrl5_c.xl_ulp_en = xl_ulp_en;
13343 ctrl6_c.xl_hm_mode = xl_hm_mode;
13344 ctrl7_g.g_hm_mode = g_hm_mode;
13345 ctrl2_g.odr_g = odr_gy;
13346 ctrl2_g.fs_g = (uint8_t) val->ui.gy.fs;
13347
13348 /* writing checked configuration */
13349 if (ctx != NULL)
13350 {
13351 bytecpy(&reg[0], (uint8_t *)&ctrl1_xl);
13352 bytecpy(&reg[1], (uint8_t *)&ctrl2_g);
13353 bytecpy(&reg[2], (uint8_t *)&ctrl3_c);
13354 bytecpy(&reg[3], (uint8_t *)&ctrl4_c);
13355 bytecpy(&reg[4], (uint8_t *)&ctrl5_c);
13356 bytecpy(&reg[5], (uint8_t *)&ctrl6_c);
13357 bytecpy(&reg[6], (uint8_t *)&ctrl7_g);
13358 bytecpy(&reg[7], (uint8_t *)&ctrl8_xl);
13359
13360 if (ret == 0)
13361 {
13362 ret = lsm6dsox_write_reg(ctx, LSM6DSOX_CTRL1_XL, (uint8_t *)&reg, 8);
13363 }
13364
13365 if (ret == 0)
13366 {
13367 ret = lsm6dsox_write_reg(ctx, LSM6DSOX_FUNC_CFG_ACCESS,
13368 (uint8_t *)&func_cfg_access, 1);
13369 }
13370 }
13371
13372 /* writing OIS checked configuration */
13373 if (aux_ctx != NULL)
13374 {
13375 bytecpy(&reg[0], (uint8_t *)&spi2_ctrl1_ois);
13376 bytecpy(&reg[1], (uint8_t *)&spi2_ctrl2_ois);
13377 bytecpy(&reg[2], (uint8_t *)&spi2_ctrl3_ois);
13378
13379 if (ret == 0)
13380 {
13381 ret = lsm6dsox_write_reg(aux_ctx, LSM6DSOX_SPI2_CTRL1_OIS, reg, 3);
13382 }
13383 }
13384
13385 else
13386 {
13387 if (ctx != NULL)
13388 {
13389 bytecpy(&reg[0], (uint8_t *)&ui_ctrl1_ois);
13390 bytecpy(&reg[1], (uint8_t *)&ui_ctrl2_ois);
13391 bytecpy(&reg[2], (uint8_t *)&ui_ctrl3_ois);
13392
13393 if (ret == 0)
13394 {
13395 ret = lsm6dsox_write_reg(ctx, LSM6DSOX_UI_CTRL1_OIS, reg, 3);
13396 }
13397 }
13398 }
13399
13400 return ret;
13401}
13402
13414int32_t lsm6dsox_mode_get(stmdev_ctx_t *ctx, stmdev_ctx_t *aux_ctx,
13415 lsm6dsox_md_t *val)
13416{
13417 lsm6dsox_emb_func_odr_cfg_b_t emb_func_odr_cfg_b;
13418 lsm6dsox_emb_func_odr_cfg_c_t emb_func_odr_cfg_c;
13419 lsm6dsox_func_cfg_access_t func_cfg_access;
13420 lsm6dsox_spi2_ctrl1_ois_t spi2_ctrl1_ois;
13421 lsm6dsox_spi2_ctrl2_ois_t spi2_ctrl2_ois;
13422 lsm6dsox_spi2_ctrl3_ois_t spi2_ctrl3_ois;
13423 lsm6dsox_emb_func_en_b_t emb_func_en_b;
13424 lsm6dsox_ui_ctrl1_ois_t ui_ctrl1_ois;
13425 lsm6dsox_ui_ctrl2_ois_t ui_ctrl2_ois;
13426 lsm6dsox_ui_ctrl3_ois_t ui_ctrl3_ois;
13427 lsm6dsox_fsm_enable_a_t fsm_enable_a;
13428 lsm6dsox_fsm_enable_b_t fsm_enable_b;
13429 lsm6dsox_ctrl1_xl_t ctrl1_xl;
13430 lsm6dsox_ctrl2_g_t ctrl2_g;
13431 lsm6dsox_ctrl3_c_t ctrl3_c;
13432 lsm6dsox_ctrl4_c_t ctrl4_c;
13433 lsm6dsox_ctrl5_c_t ctrl5_c;
13434 lsm6dsox_ctrl6_c_t ctrl6_c;
13435 lsm6dsox_ctrl7_g_t ctrl7_g;
13436 uint8_t reg[8];
13437 int32_t ret;
13438
13439 ret = 0;
13440
13441 /* reading the registers of the device */
13442 if (ctx != NULL)
13443 {
13444 ret = lsm6dsox_read_reg(ctx, LSM6DSOX_CTRL1_XL, reg, 7);
13445 bytecpy((uint8_t *)&ctrl1_xl, &reg[0]);
13446 bytecpy((uint8_t *)&ctrl2_g, &reg[1]);
13447 bytecpy((uint8_t *)&ctrl3_c, &reg[2]);
13448 bytecpy((uint8_t *)&ctrl4_c, &reg[3]);
13449 bytecpy((uint8_t *)&ctrl5_c, &reg[4]);
13450 bytecpy((uint8_t *)&ctrl6_c, &reg[5]);
13451 bytecpy((uint8_t *)&ctrl7_g, &reg[6]);
13452
13453 if (ret == 0)
13454 {
13455 ret = lsm6dsox_read_reg(ctx, LSM6DSOX_FUNC_CFG_ACCESS,
13456 (uint8_t *)&func_cfg_access, 1);
13457 }
13458
13459 if (ret == 0)
13460 {
13461 ret = lsm6dsox_mem_bank_set(ctx, LSM6DSOX_EMBEDDED_FUNC_BANK);
13462 }
13463
13464 if (ret == 0)
13465 {
13466 ret = lsm6dsox_read_reg(ctx, LSM6DSOX_EMB_FUNC_ODR_CFG_B, reg, 2);
13467 bytecpy((uint8_t *)&emb_func_odr_cfg_b, &reg[0]);
13468 bytecpy((uint8_t *)&emb_func_odr_cfg_c, &reg[1]);
13469 }
13470
13471 if (ret == 0)
13472 {
13473 ret = lsm6dsox_read_reg(ctx, LSM6DSOX_EMB_FUNC_EN_B,
13474 (uint8_t *)&emb_func_en_b, 1);
13475 }
13476
13477 if (ret == 0)
13478 {
13479 ret = lsm6dsox_read_reg(ctx, LSM6DSOX_FSM_ENABLE_A, reg, 2);
13480 bytecpy((uint8_t *)&fsm_enable_a, &reg[0]);
13481 bytecpy((uint8_t *)&fsm_enable_b, &reg[1]);
13482 }
13483
13484 if (ret == 0)
13485 {
13486 ret = lsm6dsox_mem_bank_set(ctx, LSM6DSOX_USER_BANK);
13487 }
13488 }
13489
13490 if (aux_ctx != NULL)
13491 {
13492 if (ret == 0)
13493 {
13494 ret = lsm6dsox_read_reg(aux_ctx, LSM6DSOX_SPI2_CTRL1_OIS, reg, 3);
13495 }
13496
13497 bytecpy((uint8_t *)&spi2_ctrl1_ois, &reg[0]);
13498 bytecpy((uint8_t *)&spi2_ctrl2_ois, &reg[1]);
13499 bytecpy((uint8_t *)&spi2_ctrl3_ois, &reg[2]);
13500 }
13501
13502 else
13503 {
13504 if (ctx != NULL)
13505 {
13506 if (ret == 0)
13507 {
13508 ret = lsm6dsox_read_reg(ctx, LSM6DSOX_UI_CTRL1_OIS, reg, 3);
13509 }
13510
13511 bytecpy((uint8_t *)&ui_ctrl1_ois, &reg[0]);
13512 bytecpy((uint8_t *)&ui_ctrl2_ois, &reg[1]);
13513 bytecpy((uint8_t *)&ui_ctrl3_ois, &reg[2]);
13514 }
13515 }
13516
13517 /* fill the input structure */
13518
13519 /* get accelerometer configuration */
13520 switch ((ctrl5_c.xl_ulp_en << 5) | (ctrl6_c.xl_hm_mode << 4) |
13521 ctrl1_xl.odr_xl)
13522 {
13523 case LSM6DSOX_XL_UI_OFF:
13524 val->ui.xl.odr = LSM6DSOX_XL_UI_OFF;
13525 break;
13526
13527 case LSM6DSOX_XL_UI_12Hz5_HP:
13528 val->ui.xl.odr = LSM6DSOX_XL_UI_12Hz5_HP;
13529 break;
13530
13531 case LSM6DSOX_XL_UI_26Hz_HP:
13532 val->ui.xl.odr = LSM6DSOX_XL_UI_26Hz_HP;
13533 break;
13534
13535 case LSM6DSOX_XL_UI_52Hz_HP:
13536 val->ui.xl.odr = LSM6DSOX_XL_UI_52Hz_HP;
13537 break;
13538
13539 case LSM6DSOX_XL_UI_104Hz_HP:
13540 val->ui.xl.odr = LSM6DSOX_XL_UI_104Hz_HP;
13541 break;
13542
13543 case LSM6DSOX_XL_UI_208Hz_HP:
13544 val->ui.xl.odr = LSM6DSOX_XL_UI_208Hz_HP;
13545 break;
13546
13547 case LSM6DSOX_XL_UI_416Hz_HP:
13548 val->ui.xl.odr = LSM6DSOX_XL_UI_416Hz_HP;
13549 break;
13550
13551 case LSM6DSOX_XL_UI_833Hz_HP:
13552 val->ui.xl.odr = LSM6DSOX_XL_UI_833Hz_HP;
13553 break;
13554
13555 case LSM6DSOX_XL_UI_1667Hz_HP:
13556 val->ui.xl.odr = LSM6DSOX_XL_UI_1667Hz_HP;
13557 break;
13558
13559 case LSM6DSOX_XL_UI_3333Hz_HP:
13560 val->ui.xl.odr = LSM6DSOX_XL_UI_3333Hz_HP;
13561 break;
13562
13563 case LSM6DSOX_XL_UI_6667Hz_HP:
13564 val->ui.xl.odr = LSM6DSOX_XL_UI_6667Hz_HP;
13565 break;
13566
13567 case LSM6DSOX_XL_UI_1Hz6_LP:
13568 val->ui.xl.odr = LSM6DSOX_XL_UI_1Hz6_LP;
13569 break;
13570
13571 case LSM6DSOX_XL_UI_12Hz5_LP:
13572 val->ui.xl.odr = LSM6DSOX_XL_UI_12Hz5_LP;
13573 break;
13574
13575 case LSM6DSOX_XL_UI_26Hz_LP:
13576 val->ui.xl.odr = LSM6DSOX_XL_UI_26Hz_LP;
13577 break;
13578
13579 case LSM6DSOX_XL_UI_52Hz_LP:
13580 val->ui.xl.odr = LSM6DSOX_XL_UI_52Hz_LP;
13581 break;
13582
13583 case LSM6DSOX_XL_UI_104Hz_NM:
13584 val->ui.xl.odr = LSM6DSOX_XL_UI_104Hz_NM;
13585 break;
13586
13587 case LSM6DSOX_XL_UI_208Hz_NM:
13588 val->ui.xl.odr = LSM6DSOX_XL_UI_208Hz_NM;
13589 break;
13590
13591 case LSM6DSOX_XL_UI_1Hz6_ULP:
13592 val->ui.xl.odr = LSM6DSOX_XL_UI_1Hz6_ULP;
13593 break;
13594
13595 case LSM6DSOX_XL_UI_12Hz5_ULP:
13596 val->ui.xl.odr = LSM6DSOX_XL_UI_12Hz5_ULP;
13597 break;
13598
13599 case LSM6DSOX_XL_UI_26Hz_ULP:
13600 val->ui.xl.odr = LSM6DSOX_XL_UI_26Hz_ULP;
13601 break;
13602
13603 case LSM6DSOX_XL_UI_52Hz_ULP:
13604 val->ui.xl.odr = LSM6DSOX_XL_UI_52Hz_ULP;
13605 break;
13606
13607 case LSM6DSOX_XL_UI_104Hz_ULP:
13608 val->ui.xl.odr = LSM6DSOX_XL_UI_104Hz_ULP;
13609 break;
13610
13611 case LSM6DSOX_XL_UI_208Hz_ULP:
13612 val->ui.xl.odr = LSM6DSOX_XL_UI_208Hz_ULP;
13613 break;
13614
13615 default:
13616 val->ui.xl.odr = LSM6DSOX_XL_UI_OFF;
13617 break;
13618 }
13619
13620 switch (ctrl1_xl.fs_xl)
13621 {
13622 case LSM6DSOX_XL_UI_2g:
13623 val->ui.xl.fs = LSM6DSOX_XL_UI_2g;
13624 break;
13625
13626 case LSM6DSOX_XL_UI_4g:
13627 val->ui.xl.fs = LSM6DSOX_XL_UI_4g;
13628 break;
13629
13630 case LSM6DSOX_XL_UI_8g:
13631 val->ui.xl.fs = LSM6DSOX_XL_UI_8g;
13632 break;
13633
13634 case LSM6DSOX_XL_UI_16g:
13635 val->ui.xl.fs = LSM6DSOX_XL_UI_16g;
13636 break;
13637
13638 default:
13639 val->ui.xl.fs = LSM6DSOX_XL_UI_2g;
13640 break;
13641 }
13642
13643 /* get gyroscope configuration */
13644 switch ((ctrl7_g.g_hm_mode << 4) | ctrl2_g.odr_g)
13645 {
13646 case LSM6DSOX_GY_UI_OFF:
13647 val->ui.gy.odr = LSM6DSOX_GY_UI_OFF;
13648 break;
13649
13650 case LSM6DSOX_GY_UI_12Hz5_LP:
13651 val->ui.gy.odr = LSM6DSOX_GY_UI_12Hz5_LP;
13652 break;
13653
13654 case LSM6DSOX_GY_UI_12Hz5_HP:
13655 val->ui.gy.odr = LSM6DSOX_GY_UI_12Hz5_HP;
13656 break;
13657
13658 case LSM6DSOX_GY_UI_26Hz_LP:
13659 val->ui.gy.odr = LSM6DSOX_GY_UI_26Hz_LP;
13660 break;
13661
13662 case LSM6DSOX_GY_UI_26Hz_HP:
13663 val->ui.gy.odr = LSM6DSOX_GY_UI_26Hz_HP;
13664 break;
13665
13666 case LSM6DSOX_GY_UI_52Hz_LP:
13667 val->ui.gy.odr = LSM6DSOX_GY_UI_52Hz_LP;
13668 break;
13669
13670 case LSM6DSOX_GY_UI_52Hz_HP:
13671 val->ui.gy.odr = LSM6DSOX_GY_UI_52Hz_HP;
13672 break;
13673
13674 case LSM6DSOX_GY_UI_104Hz_NM:
13675 val->ui.gy.odr = LSM6DSOX_GY_UI_104Hz_NM;
13676 break;
13677
13678 case LSM6DSOX_GY_UI_104Hz_HP:
13679 val->ui.gy.odr = LSM6DSOX_GY_UI_104Hz_HP;
13680 break;
13681
13682 case LSM6DSOX_GY_UI_208Hz_NM:
13683 val->ui.gy.odr = LSM6DSOX_GY_UI_208Hz_NM;
13684 break;
13685
13686 case LSM6DSOX_GY_UI_208Hz_HP:
13687 val->ui.gy.odr = LSM6DSOX_GY_UI_208Hz_HP;
13688 break;
13689
13690 case LSM6DSOX_GY_UI_416Hz_HP:
13691 val->ui.gy.odr = LSM6DSOX_GY_UI_416Hz_HP;
13692 break;
13693
13694 case LSM6DSOX_GY_UI_833Hz_HP:
13695 val->ui.gy.odr = LSM6DSOX_GY_UI_833Hz_HP;
13696 break;
13697
13698 case LSM6DSOX_GY_UI_1667Hz_HP:
13699 val->ui.gy.odr = LSM6DSOX_GY_UI_1667Hz_HP;
13700 break;
13701
13702 case LSM6DSOX_GY_UI_3333Hz_HP:
13703 val->ui.gy.odr = LSM6DSOX_GY_UI_3333Hz_HP;
13704 break;
13705
13706 case LSM6DSOX_GY_UI_6667Hz_HP:
13707 val->ui.gy.odr = LSM6DSOX_GY_UI_6667Hz_HP;
13708 break;
13709
13710 default:
13711 val->ui.gy.odr = LSM6DSOX_GY_UI_OFF;
13712 break;
13713 }
13714
13715 switch (ctrl2_g.fs_g)
13716 {
13717 case LSM6DSOX_GY_UI_125dps:
13718 val->ui.gy.fs = LSM6DSOX_GY_UI_125dps;
13719 break;
13720
13721 case LSM6DSOX_GY_UI_250dps:
13722 val->ui.gy.fs = LSM6DSOX_GY_UI_250dps;
13723 break;
13724
13725 case LSM6DSOX_GY_UI_500dps:
13726 val->ui.gy.fs = LSM6DSOX_GY_UI_500dps;
13727 break;
13728
13729 case LSM6DSOX_GY_UI_1000dps:
13730 val->ui.gy.fs = LSM6DSOX_GY_UI_1000dps;
13731 break;
13732
13733 case LSM6DSOX_GY_UI_2000dps:
13734 val->ui.gy.fs = LSM6DSOX_GY_UI_2000dps;
13735 break;
13736
13737 default:
13738 val->ui.gy.fs = LSM6DSOX_GY_UI_125dps;
13739 break;
13740 }
13741
13742 /* get finite state machine configuration */
13743 if ((fsm_enable_a.fsm1_en | fsm_enable_a.fsm2_en |
13744 fsm_enable_a.fsm3_en |
13745 fsm_enable_a.fsm4_en | fsm_enable_a.fsm5_en | fsm_enable_a.fsm6_en |
13746 fsm_enable_a.fsm7_en | fsm_enable_a.fsm8_en | fsm_enable_b.fsm9_en |
13747 fsm_enable_b.fsm10_en | fsm_enable_b.fsm11_en |
13748 fsm_enable_b.fsm12_en | fsm_enable_b.fsm13_en |
13749 fsm_enable_b.fsm14_en | fsm_enable_b.fsm15_en |
13750 fsm_enable_b.fsm16_en) == PROPERTY_ENABLE)
13751 {
13752 switch (emb_func_odr_cfg_b.fsm_odr)
13753 {
13754 case LSM6DSOX_FSM_12Hz5:
13755 val->fsm.odr = LSM6DSOX_FSM_12Hz5;
13756 break;
13757
13758 case LSM6DSOX_FSM_26Hz:
13759 val->fsm.odr = LSM6DSOX_FSM_26Hz;
13760 break;
13761
13762 case LSM6DSOX_FSM_52Hz:
13763 val->fsm.odr = LSM6DSOX_FSM_52Hz;
13764 break;
13765
13766 case LSM6DSOX_FSM_104Hz:
13767 val->fsm.odr = LSM6DSOX_FSM_104Hz;
13768 break;
13769
13770 default:
13771 val->fsm.odr = LSM6DSOX_FSM_12Hz5;
13772 break;
13773 }
13774
13775 val->fsm.sens = LSM6DSOX_FSM_XL_GY;
13776
13777 if (val->ui.gy.odr == LSM6DSOX_GY_UI_OFF)
13778 {
13779 val->fsm.sens = LSM6DSOX_FSM_XL;
13780 }
13781
13782 if (val->ui.xl.odr == LSM6DSOX_XL_UI_OFF)
13783 {
13784 val->fsm.sens = LSM6DSOX_FSM_GY;
13785 }
13786 }
13787
13788 else
13789 {
13790 val->fsm.sens = LSM6DSOX_FSM_DISABLE;
13791 }
13792
13793 /* get machine learning core configuration */
13794 if (emb_func_en_b.mlc_en == PROPERTY_ENABLE)
13795 {
13796 switch (emb_func_odr_cfg_c.mlc_odr)
13797 {
13798 case LSM6DSOX_MLC_12Hz5:
13799 val->mlc.odr = LSM6DSOX_MLC_12Hz5;
13800 break;
13801
13802 case LSM6DSOX_MLC_26Hz:
13803 val->mlc.odr = LSM6DSOX_MLC_26Hz;
13804 break;
13805
13806 case LSM6DSOX_MLC_52Hz:
13807 val->mlc.odr = LSM6DSOX_MLC_52Hz;
13808 break;
13809
13810 case LSM6DSOX_MLC_104Hz:
13811 val->mlc.odr = LSM6DSOX_MLC_104Hz;
13812 break;
13813
13814 default:
13815 val->mlc.odr = LSM6DSOX_MLC_12Hz5;
13816 break;
13817 }
13818
13819 val->mlc.sens = LSM6DSOX_MLC_XL_GY;
13820
13821 if (val->ui.gy.odr == LSM6DSOX_GY_UI_OFF)
13822 {
13823 val->mlc.sens = LSM6DSOX_MLC_XL;
13824 }
13825
13826 if (val->ui.xl.odr == LSM6DSOX_XL_UI_OFF)
13827 {
13828 val->mlc.sens = LSM6DSOX_MLC_DISABLE;
13829 }
13830 }
13831
13832 else
13833 {
13834 val->mlc.sens = LSM6DSOX_MLC_DISABLE;
13835 }
13836
13837 /* get ois configuration */
13838
13839 /* OIS configuration mode */
13840 switch ((func_cfg_access.ois_ctrl_from_ui << 1) +
13841 ctrl7_g.ois_on_en)
13842 {
13843 case LSM6DSOX_OIS_ONLY_AUX:
13844 switch (spi2_ctrl3_ois.fs_xl_ois)
13845 {
13846 case LSM6DSOX_XL_OIS_2g:
13847 val->ois.xl.fs = LSM6DSOX_XL_OIS_2g;
13848 break;
13849
13850 case LSM6DSOX_XL_OIS_4g:
13851 val->ois.xl.fs = LSM6DSOX_XL_OIS_4g;
13852 break;
13853
13854 case LSM6DSOX_XL_OIS_8g:
13855 val->ois.xl.fs = LSM6DSOX_XL_OIS_8g;
13856 break;
13857
13858 case LSM6DSOX_XL_OIS_16g:
13859 val->ois.xl.fs = LSM6DSOX_XL_OIS_16g;
13860 break;
13861
13862 default:
13863 val->ois.xl.fs = LSM6DSOX_XL_OIS_2g;
13864 break;
13865 }
13866
13867 switch (spi2_ctrl1_ois.mode4_en)
13868 {
13869 case LSM6DSOX_XL_OIS_OFF:
13870 val->ois.xl.odr = LSM6DSOX_XL_OIS_OFF;
13871 break;
13872
13873 case LSM6DSOX_XL_OIS_6667Hz_HP:
13874 val->ois.xl.odr = LSM6DSOX_XL_OIS_6667Hz_HP;
13875 break;
13876
13877 default:
13878 val->ois.xl.odr = LSM6DSOX_XL_OIS_OFF;
13879 break;
13880 }
13881
13882 switch (spi2_ctrl1_ois.fs_g_ois)
13883 {
13884 case LSM6DSOX_GY_OIS_250dps:
13885 val->ois.gy.fs = LSM6DSOX_GY_OIS_250dps;
13886 break;
13887
13888 case LSM6DSOX_GY_OIS_500dps:
13889 val->ois.gy.fs = LSM6DSOX_GY_OIS_500dps;
13890 break;
13891
13892 case LSM6DSOX_GY_OIS_1000dps:
13893 val->ois.gy.fs = LSM6DSOX_GY_OIS_1000dps;
13894 break;
13895
13896 case LSM6DSOX_GY_OIS_2000dps:
13897 val->ois.gy.fs = LSM6DSOX_GY_OIS_2000dps;
13898 break;
13899
13900 default:
13901 val->ois.gy.fs = LSM6DSOX_GY_OIS_250dps;
13902 break;
13903 }
13904
13905 switch (spi2_ctrl1_ois.ois_en_spi2)
13906 {
13907 case LSM6DSOX_GY_OIS_OFF:
13908 val->ois.gy.odr = LSM6DSOX_GY_OIS_OFF;
13909 break;
13910
13911 case LSM6DSOX_GY_OIS_6667Hz_HP:
13912 val->ois.gy.odr = LSM6DSOX_GY_OIS_6667Hz_HP;
13913 break;
13914
13915 default:
13916 val->ois.gy.odr = LSM6DSOX_GY_OIS_OFF;
13917 break;
13918 }
13919
13920 val->ois.ctrl_md = LSM6DSOX_OIS_ONLY_AUX;
13921 break;
13922
13923 case LSM6DSOX_OIS_ONLY_UI:
13924 switch (ui_ctrl3_ois.fs_xl_ois)
13925 {
13926 case LSM6DSOX_XL_OIS_2g:
13927 val->ois.xl.fs = LSM6DSOX_XL_OIS_2g;
13928 break;
13929
13930 case LSM6DSOX_XL_OIS_4g:
13931 val->ois.xl.fs = LSM6DSOX_XL_OIS_4g;
13932 break;
13933
13934 case LSM6DSOX_XL_OIS_8g:
13935 val->ois.xl.fs = LSM6DSOX_XL_OIS_8g;
13936 break;
13937
13938 case LSM6DSOX_XL_OIS_16g:
13939 val->ois.xl.fs = LSM6DSOX_XL_OIS_16g;
13940 break;
13941
13942 default:
13943 val->ois.xl.fs = LSM6DSOX_XL_OIS_2g;
13944 break;
13945 }
13946
13947 switch (ui_ctrl1_ois.ois_en_spi2)
13948 {
13949 case LSM6DSOX_GY_OIS_OFF:
13950 val->ois.gy.odr = LSM6DSOX_GY_OIS_OFF;
13951 break;
13952
13953 case LSM6DSOX_GY_OIS_6667Hz_HP:
13954 val->ois.gy.odr = LSM6DSOX_GY_OIS_6667Hz_HP;
13955 break;
13956
13957 default:
13958 val->ois.gy.odr = LSM6DSOX_GY_OIS_OFF;
13959 break;
13960 }
13961
13962 switch (ui_ctrl1_ois.fs_g_ois)
13963 {
13964 case LSM6DSOX_GY_OIS_250dps:
13965 val->ois.gy.fs = LSM6DSOX_GY_OIS_250dps;
13966 break;
13967
13968 case LSM6DSOX_GY_OIS_125dps:
13969 val->ois.gy.fs = LSM6DSOX_GY_OIS_125dps;
13970 break;
13971
13972 case LSM6DSOX_GY_OIS_500dps:
13973 val->ois.gy.fs = LSM6DSOX_GY_OIS_500dps;
13974 break;
13975
13976 case LSM6DSOX_GY_OIS_1000dps:
13977 val->ois.gy.fs = LSM6DSOX_GY_OIS_1000dps;
13978 break;
13979
13980 case LSM6DSOX_GY_OIS_2000dps:
13981 val->ois.gy.fs = LSM6DSOX_GY_OIS_2000dps;
13982 break;
13983
13984 default:
13985 val->ois.gy.fs = LSM6DSOX_GY_OIS_250dps;
13986 break;
13987 }
13988
13989 switch (ui_ctrl1_ois.mode4_en)
13990 {
13991 case LSM6DSOX_XL_OIS_OFF:
13992 val->ois.xl.odr = LSM6DSOX_XL_OIS_OFF;
13993 break;
13994
13995 case LSM6DSOX_XL_OIS_6667Hz_HP:
13996 val->ois.xl.odr = LSM6DSOX_XL_OIS_6667Hz_HP;
13997 break;
13998
13999 default:
14000 val->ois.xl.odr = LSM6DSOX_XL_OIS_OFF;
14001 break;
14002 }
14003
14004 val->ois.ctrl_md = LSM6DSOX_OIS_ONLY_UI;
14005 break;
14006
14007 case LSM6DSOX_OIS_MIXED:
14008 switch (spi2_ctrl3_ois.fs_xl_ois)
14009 {
14010 case LSM6DSOX_XL_OIS_2g:
14011 val->ois.xl.fs = LSM6DSOX_XL_OIS_2g;
14012 break;
14013
14014 case LSM6DSOX_XL_OIS_4g:
14015 val->ois.xl.fs = LSM6DSOX_XL_OIS_4g;
14016 break;
14017
14018 case LSM6DSOX_XL_OIS_8g:
14019 val->ois.xl.fs = LSM6DSOX_XL_OIS_8g;
14020 break;
14021
14022 case LSM6DSOX_XL_OIS_16g:
14023 val->ois.xl.fs = LSM6DSOX_XL_OIS_16g;
14024 break;
14025
14026 default:
14027 val->ois.xl.fs = LSM6DSOX_XL_OIS_2g;
14028 break;
14029 }
14030
14031 switch (spi2_ctrl1_ois.mode4_en)
14032 {
14033 case LSM6DSOX_XL_OIS_OFF:
14034 val->ois.xl.odr = LSM6DSOX_XL_OIS_OFF;
14035 break;
14036
14037 case LSM6DSOX_XL_OIS_6667Hz_HP:
14038 val->ois.xl.odr = LSM6DSOX_XL_OIS_6667Hz_HP;
14039 break;
14040
14041 default:
14042 val->ois.xl.odr = LSM6DSOX_XL_OIS_OFF;
14043 break;
14044 }
14045
14046 switch (spi2_ctrl1_ois.fs_g_ois)
14047 {
14048 case LSM6DSOX_GY_OIS_250dps:
14049 val->ois.gy.fs = LSM6DSOX_GY_OIS_250dps;
14050 break;
14051
14052 case LSM6DSOX_GY_OIS_500dps:
14053 val->ois.gy.fs = LSM6DSOX_GY_OIS_500dps;
14054 break;
14055
14056 case LSM6DSOX_GY_OIS_1000dps:
14057 val->ois.gy.fs = LSM6DSOX_GY_OIS_1000dps;
14058 break;
14059
14060 case LSM6DSOX_GY_OIS_2000dps:
14061 val->ois.gy.fs = LSM6DSOX_GY_OIS_2000dps;
14062 break;
14063
14064 default:
14065 val->ois.gy.fs = LSM6DSOX_GY_OIS_250dps;
14066 break;
14067 }
14068
14069 switch (ui_ctrl1_ois.ois_en_spi2)
14070 {
14071 case LSM6DSOX_GY_OIS_OFF:
14072 val->ois.gy.odr = LSM6DSOX_GY_OIS_OFF;
14073 break;
14074
14075 case LSM6DSOX_GY_OIS_6667Hz_HP:
14076 val->ois.gy.odr = LSM6DSOX_GY_OIS_6667Hz_HP;
14077 break;
14078
14079 default:
14080 val->ois.gy.odr = LSM6DSOX_GY_OIS_OFF;
14081 break;
14082 }
14083
14084 val->ois.ctrl_md = LSM6DSOX_OIS_MIXED;
14085 break;
14086
14087 default:
14088 spi2_ctrl1_ois.fs_g_ois = (uint8_t)val->ois.gy.fs;
14089 spi2_ctrl1_ois.ois_en_spi2 = (uint8_t)val->ois.gy.odr |
14090 (uint8_t)val->ois.xl.odr;
14091 spi2_ctrl1_ois.mode4_en = (uint8_t) val->ois.xl.odr;
14092 spi2_ctrl3_ois.fs_xl_ois = (uint8_t)val->ois.xl.fs;
14093 val->ois.ctrl_md = LSM6DSOX_OIS_ONLY_AUX;
14094 break;
14095 }
14096
14097 return ret;
14098}
14099
14108int32_t lsm6dsox_data_get(stmdev_ctx_t *ctx, stmdev_ctx_t *aux_ctx,
14109 lsm6dsox_md_t *md, lsm6dsox_data_t *data)
14110{
14111 uint8_t buff[14];
14112 int32_t ret;
14113
14114 uint8_t i;
14115 uint8_t j;
14116 ret = 0;
14117
14118 /* read data */
14119 if (ctx != NULL)
14120 {
14121 ret = lsm6dsox_read_reg(ctx, LSM6DSOX_OUT_TEMP_L, buff, 14);
14122 }
14123
14124 j = 0;
14125 /* temperature conversion */
14126 data->ui.heat.raw = (int16_t)buff[j + 1U];
14127 data->ui.heat.raw = (((int16_t)data->ui.heat.raw * (int16_t)256) +
14128 (int16_t)buff[j]);
14129 j += 2U;
14130 data->ui.heat.deg_c = lsm6dsox_from_lsb_to_celsius((
14131 int16_t)data->ui.heat.raw);
14132
14133 /* angular rate conversion */
14134 for (i = 0U; i < 3U; i++)
14135 {
14136 data->ui.gy.raw[i] = (int16_t)buff[j + 1U];
14137 data->ui.gy.raw[i] = (data->ui.gy.raw[i] * 256) + (int16_t) buff[j];
14138 j += 2U;
14139
14140 switch (md->ui.gy.fs)
14141 {
14142 case LSM6DSOX_GY_UI_250dps:
14143 data->ui.gy.mdps[i] = lsm6dsox_from_fs250_to_mdps(data->ui.gy.raw[i]);
14144 break;
14145
14146 case LSM6DSOX_GY_UI_125dps:
14147 data->ui.gy.mdps[i] = lsm6dsox_from_fs125_to_mdps(data->ui.gy.raw[i]);
14148 break;
14149
14150 case LSM6DSOX_GY_UI_500dps:
14151 data->ui.gy.mdps[i] = lsm6dsox_from_fs500_to_mdps(data->ui.gy.raw[i]);
14152 break;
14153
14154 case LSM6DSOX_GY_UI_1000dps:
14155 data->ui.gy.mdps[i] = lsm6dsox_from_fs1000_to_mdps(
14156 data->ui.gy.raw[i]);
14157 break;
14158
14159 case LSM6DSOX_GY_UI_2000dps:
14160 data->ui.gy.mdps[i] = lsm6dsox_from_fs2000_to_mdps(
14161 data->ui.gy.raw[i]);
14162 break;
14163
14164 default:
14165 data->ui.gy.mdps[i] = 0.0f;
14166 break;
14167 }
14168 }
14169
14170 /* acceleration conversion */
14171 for (i = 0U; i < 3U; i++)
14172 {
14173 data->ui.xl.raw[i] = (int16_t)buff[j + 1U];
14174 data->ui.xl.raw[i] = (data->ui.xl.raw[i] * 256) + (int16_t) buff[j];
14175 j += 2U;
14176
14177 switch (md->ui.xl.fs)
14178 {
14179 case LSM6DSOX_XL_UI_2g:
14180 data->ui.xl.mg[i] = lsm6dsox_from_fs2_to_mg(data->ui.xl.raw[i]);
14181 break;
14182
14183 case LSM6DSOX_XL_UI_4g:
14184 data->ui.xl.mg[i] = lsm6dsox_from_fs4_to_mg(data->ui.xl.raw[i]);
14185 break;
14186
14187 case LSM6DSOX_XL_UI_8g:
14188 data->ui.xl.mg[i] = lsm6dsox_from_fs8_to_mg(data->ui.xl.raw[i]);
14189 break;
14190
14191 case LSM6DSOX_XL_UI_16g:
14192 data->ui.xl.mg[i] = lsm6dsox_from_fs16_to_mg(data->ui.xl.raw[i]);
14193 break;
14194
14195 default:
14196 data->ui.xl.mg[i] = 0.0f;
14197 break;
14198 }
14199 }
14200
14201 /* read data from ois chain */
14202 if (aux_ctx != NULL)
14203 {
14204 if (ret == 0)
14205 {
14206 ret = lsm6dsox_read_reg(aux_ctx, LSM6DSOX_SPI2_OUTX_L_G_OIS, buff,
14207 12);
14208 }
14209 }
14210
14211 else
14212 {
14213 if ((ctx != NULL) && (md->ois.ctrl_md == LSM6DSOX_OIS_ONLY_UI))
14214 {
14215 ret = lsm6dsox_read_reg(ctx, LSM6DSOX_UI_OUTX_L_G_OIS, buff, 12);
14216 }
14217 }
14218
14219 j = 0;
14220
14221 /* ois angular rate conversion */
14222 for (i = 0U; i < 3U; i++)
14223 {
14224 data->ois.gy.raw[i] = (int16_t) buff[j + 1U];
14225 data->ois.gy.raw[i] = (data->ois.gy.raw[i] * 256) + (int16_t) buff[j];
14226 j += 2U;
14227
14228 switch (md->ois.gy.fs)
14229 {
14230 case LSM6DSOX_GY_UI_250dps:
14231 data->ois.gy.mdps[i] = lsm6dsox_from_fs250_to_mdps(
14232 data->ois.gy.raw[i]);
14233 break;
14234
14235 case LSM6DSOX_GY_UI_125dps:
14236 data->ois.gy.mdps[i] = lsm6dsox_from_fs125_to_mdps(
14237 data->ois.gy.raw[i]);
14238 break;
14239
14240 case LSM6DSOX_GY_UI_500dps:
14241 data->ois.gy.mdps[i] = lsm6dsox_from_fs500_to_mdps(
14242 data->ois.gy.raw[i]);
14243 break;
14244
14245 case LSM6DSOX_GY_UI_1000dps:
14246 data->ois.gy.mdps[i] = lsm6dsox_from_fs1000_to_mdps(
14247 data->ois.gy.raw[i]);
14248 break;
14249
14250 case LSM6DSOX_GY_UI_2000dps:
14251 data->ois.gy.mdps[i] = lsm6dsox_from_fs2000_to_mdps(
14252 data->ois.gy.raw[i]);
14253 break;
14254
14255 default:
14256 data->ois.gy.mdps[i] = 0.0f;
14257 break;
14258 }
14259 }
14260
14261 /* ois acceleration conversion */
14262 for (i = 0U; i < 3U; i++)
14263 {
14264 data->ois.xl.raw[i] = (int16_t) buff[j + 1U];
14265 data->ois.xl.raw[i] = (data->ois.xl.raw[i] * 256) + (int16_t) buff[j];
14266 j += 2U;
14267
14268 switch (md->ois.xl.fs)
14269 {
14270 case LSM6DSOX_XL_UI_2g:
14271 data->ois.xl.mg[i] = lsm6dsox_from_fs2_to_mg(data->ois.xl.raw[i]);
14272 break;
14273
14274 case LSM6DSOX_XL_UI_4g:
14275 data->ois.xl.mg[i] = lsm6dsox_from_fs4_to_mg(data->ois.xl.raw[i]);
14276 break;
14277
14278 case LSM6DSOX_XL_UI_8g:
14279 data->ois.xl.mg[i] = lsm6dsox_from_fs8_to_mg(data->ois.xl.raw[i]);
14280 break;
14281
14282 case LSM6DSOX_XL_UI_16g:
14283 data->ois.xl.mg[i] = lsm6dsox_from_fs16_to_mg(data->ois.xl.raw[i]);
14284 break;
14285
14286 default:
14287 data->ois.xl.mg[i] = 0.0f;
14288 break;
14289 }
14290 }
14291
14292 return ret;
14293}
14294
14304int32_t lsm6dsox_embedded_sens_set(stmdev_ctx_t *ctx,
14305 lsm6dsox_emb_sens_t *val)
14306{
14307 lsm6dsox_emb_func_en_a_t emb_func_en_a;
14308 lsm6dsox_emb_func_en_b_t emb_func_en_b;
14309 int32_t ret;
14310
14311 ret = lsm6dsox_mem_bank_set(ctx, LSM6DSOX_EMBEDDED_FUNC_BANK);
14312
14313 if (ret == 0)
14314 {
14315 ret = lsm6dsox_read_reg(ctx, LSM6DSOX_EMB_FUNC_EN_A,
14316 (uint8_t *)&emb_func_en_a, 1);
14317 }
14318
14319 if (ret == 0)
14320 {
14321 ret = lsm6dsox_read_reg(ctx, LSM6DSOX_EMB_FUNC_EN_B,
14322 (uint8_t *)&emb_func_en_b, 1);
14323 emb_func_en_b.mlc_en = val->mlc;
14324 emb_func_en_b.fsm_en = val->fsm;
14325 emb_func_en_a.tilt_en = val->tilt;
14326 emb_func_en_a.pedo_en = val->step;
14327 emb_func_en_a.sign_motion_en = val->sig_mot;
14328 emb_func_en_b.fifo_compr_en = val->fifo_compr;
14329 }
14330
14331 if (ret == 0)
14332 {
14333 ret = lsm6dsox_write_reg(ctx, LSM6DSOX_EMB_FUNC_EN_A,
14334 (uint8_t *)&emb_func_en_a, 1);
14335 }
14336
14337 if (ret == 0)
14338 {
14339 ret = lsm6dsox_write_reg(ctx, LSM6DSOX_EMB_FUNC_EN_B,
14340 (uint8_t *)&emb_func_en_b, 1);
14341 }
14342
14343 if (ret == 0)
14344 {
14345 ret = lsm6dsox_mem_bank_set(ctx, LSM6DSOX_USER_BANK);
14346 }
14347
14348 return ret;
14349}
14350
14360int32_t lsm6dsox_embedded_sens_get(stmdev_ctx_t *ctx,
14361 lsm6dsox_emb_sens_t *emb_sens)
14362{
14363 lsm6dsox_emb_func_en_a_t emb_func_en_a;
14364 lsm6dsox_emb_func_en_b_t emb_func_en_b;
14365 int32_t ret;
14366
14367 ret = lsm6dsox_mem_bank_set(ctx, LSM6DSOX_EMBEDDED_FUNC_BANK);
14368
14369 if (ret == 0)
14370 {
14371 ret = lsm6dsox_read_reg(ctx, LSM6DSOX_EMB_FUNC_EN_A,
14372 (uint8_t *)&emb_func_en_a, 1);
14373 }
14374
14375 if (ret == 0)
14376 {
14377 ret = lsm6dsox_read_reg(ctx, LSM6DSOX_EMB_FUNC_EN_B,
14378 (uint8_t *)&emb_func_en_b, 1);
14379 emb_sens->mlc = emb_func_en_b.mlc_en;
14380 emb_sens->fsm = emb_func_en_b.fsm_en;
14381 emb_sens->tilt = emb_func_en_a.tilt_en;
14382 emb_sens->step = emb_func_en_a.pedo_en;
14383 emb_sens->sig_mot = emb_func_en_a.sign_motion_en;
14384 emb_sens->fifo_compr = emb_func_en_b.fifo_compr_en;
14385 }
14386
14387 if (ret == 0)
14388 {
14389 ret = lsm6dsox_mem_bank_set(ctx, LSM6DSOX_USER_BANK);
14390 }
14391
14392 return ret;
14393}
14394
14404int32_t lsm6dsox_embedded_sens_off(stmdev_ctx_t *ctx)
14405{
14406 lsm6dsox_emb_func_en_a_t emb_func_en_a;
14407 lsm6dsox_emb_func_en_b_t emb_func_en_b;
14408 int32_t ret;
14409
14410 ret = lsm6dsox_mem_bank_set(ctx, LSM6DSOX_EMBEDDED_FUNC_BANK);
14411
14412 if (ret == 0)
14413 {
14414 ret = lsm6dsox_read_reg(ctx, LSM6DSOX_EMB_FUNC_EN_A,
14415 (uint8_t *)&emb_func_en_a, 1);
14416 }
14417
14418 if (ret == 0)
14419 {
14420 ret = lsm6dsox_read_reg(ctx, LSM6DSOX_EMB_FUNC_EN_B,
14421 (uint8_t *)&emb_func_en_b, 1);
14422 emb_func_en_b.mlc_en = PROPERTY_DISABLE;
14423 emb_func_en_b.fsm_en = PROPERTY_DISABLE;
14424 emb_func_en_a.tilt_en = PROPERTY_DISABLE;
14425 emb_func_en_a.pedo_en = PROPERTY_DISABLE;
14426 emb_func_en_a.sign_motion_en = PROPERTY_DISABLE;
14427 emb_func_en_b.fifo_compr_en = PROPERTY_DISABLE;
14428 }
14429
14430 if (ret == 0)
14431 {
14432 ret = lsm6dsox_write_reg(ctx, LSM6DSOX_EMB_FUNC_EN_A,
14433 (uint8_t *)&emb_func_en_a, 1);
14434 }
14435
14436 if (ret == 0)
14437 {
14438 ret = lsm6dsox_write_reg(ctx, LSM6DSOX_EMB_FUNC_EN_B,
14439 (uint8_t *)&emb_func_en_b, 1);
14440 }
14441
14442 if (ret == 0)
14443 {
14444 ret = lsm6dsox_mem_bank_set(ctx, LSM6DSOX_USER_BANK);
14445 }
14446
14447 return ret;
14448}
